Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:22.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后用大量的福特零件组装而成\N{\fs100}And then it was put together using quite a lot of Ford-based parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:25.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但它仍然是一辆阿斯顿马丁\N{\fs100}But it is still an Aston Martin,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:29.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很多人认为 这辆车是从旧DB时代算起\N{\fs100}and many feel it's the first proper Aston Martin
