Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"显然"我们目前位于曼彻斯特南部\N{\fs100}Just south of Manchester, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快看这个 沙丘\N{\fs100}Ooh, look at this. Dunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}妥妥的撒哈拉\N{\fs100}Proper Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:52.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沙丘是出了名的危险\N{\fs100}Dunes are notoriously dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以我们决定做点傻事\N{\fs100}So we decided to muck about.
