Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}千万要记住\N{\fs100}There's a top tip there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不好了\N{\fs100}Oh no. Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:13.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得我的空调刚刚坏了\N{\fs100}I think my air-conditioning just packed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我真觉得坏了\N{\fs100}I genuinely think it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你这运气真是差到难以置信\N{\fs100}That is an unbelievably rotten bit of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:22.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的还能用\N{\fs100}Mine's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}外面的温度是多少\N{\fs100}What is the temperature out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}48度 我的天啊\N{\fs100}48 degrees. Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:33.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}发动机温度过高 请立即停车 \N{\fs100}High engine temp. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车让我立即停车\N{\fs100}Mine is telling me to stop immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的天啊\N{\fs100}Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:43.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嗨\N{\fs100}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}啊\N{\fs100}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}请问 先生您遇到了什么问题\N{\fs100}What seems to be the trouble, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:50.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-遇到了什么麻烦 -看这里就知道了\N{\fs100}-Having a spot of bother, are we? -A lot of it can be explained by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:52.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}原来如此\N{\fs100}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你拿的什么 -风扇\N{\fs100}-What have you got there? -A fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.28,顶端1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}彼特·琼斯: BBC商业投资真人秀《龙穴》常驻评委
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:58.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好吧 -从彼特琼斯那儿买的\N{\fs100}Right. From Peter Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}空调刚才真的坏了\N{\fs100}It really has stopped working in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:03.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在想是不是皮带掉了\N{\fs100}That's what I'm wondering, if it's lost the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这是什么 -我怀疑是冷却液\N{\fs100}-What's that? -That's coolant, I suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:08.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可能是这里流出来的\N{\fs100}that's probably come out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}奇怪的是 阿斯顿马丁自称是手工打造的\N{\fs100}And it's weird, cos it says it's handbuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 说明安装过程非常仔细\N{\fs100}-Yeah, I think... -Which means done really carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:14.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}英国纯手工打造\N{\fs100}"Handbuilt in England."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}问题出在这里\N{\fs100}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:18.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}找到原因了\N{\fs100}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:25.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-依然异常 -你什么都没修啊\N{\fs100}-It's still off the dial. -You can't just sit there. You're going to have to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我得让它冷却一下 什么都不能碰\N{\fs100}I'm going to have to let it cool, that's all I can do. I can't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你得修好啊 -为什么不能碰\N{\fs100}-You've got to mend it. -Why can't you touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为非常烫\N{\fs100}Because it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以你打算等凉下来了再修\N{\fs100}So you wait for it to cool down, then take the engine out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不可能啊 环境温度都49\N{\fs100}It'll never cool down. It's 49 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:37.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}仪表已经爆表了\N{\fs100}It's right at the top of the gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不是 我是说外部温度\N{\fs100}No, no, no. External temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:42.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}63度\N{\fs100}63.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:47.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-什么单位 华氏吗 -华氏度 -不可能是60华氏度\N{\fs100}-What, that's Fahrenheit? -Fahrenheit, yes. -Well, it's not 60. -That's a summer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:48.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这辆车还以为我们在诺丁汉\N{\fs100}This thinks it's in Nottingham.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.84,0:23:50.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别笑 你看嘛\N{\fs100}It does, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:54.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}华氏度63 定位在诺丁汉\N{\fs100}It's 63 degrees Fahrenheit and it's in Nottingham.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:55.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这车就是这么认为的\N{\fs100}That's what it thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 我们该怎么办\N{\fs100}So, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:02.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}鉴于哈蒙德有房有车\N{\fs100}Given that Hammond had a house and a car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:06.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且他的车以为自己身处东米德兰 沐浴着春光\N{\fs100}which believed it was in the East Midlands on a nice spring day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:09.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以我决定不把电风扇给他\N{\fs100}I decided not to give him my fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后转身离开\N{\fs100}And then we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:27.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}情况简报 我们已经出发了15分钟\N{\fs100}OK, sitrep. We've done 15 minutes of travel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.32,0:24:29.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只有两辆车正常行驶\N{\fs100}and two of us are still moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:37.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}幸运的是 我很快找到了问题所在\N{\fs100}Mercifully, I worked out what was wrong quite quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:41.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我之前以为这些液体是冷却液\N{\fs100}This fluid that I thought was coolant from the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.16,0:24:43.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它们沸腾后溢出\N{\fs100}that had boiled over and come out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.72,0:24:44.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但其实不是冷却液\N{\fs100}isn't engine coolant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.80,0:24:47.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而是转向助力油 是从这里流出来的\N{\fs100}It's power steering fluid. It's come out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:50.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沸腾的原因是发动机舱里太热了\N{\fs100}That just got hot and boiled because it was so hot in the engine bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.76,0:24:52.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我急需散热\N{\fs100}I need to get heat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.76,0:24:55.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}对了 威尔曼先生的备用货车\N{\fs100}Right, Mr Wilman's backup van.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.20,0:24:58.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}里面肯定有工具\N{\fs100}There must be tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:04.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}开玩笑吗 我希望用不到这个\N{\fs100}Really? God, I hope I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.80,0:25:07.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}慢着 这个行吗\N{\fs100}Oh, hang on. Tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:08.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了\N{\fs100}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.88,0:25:14.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这样做让我很痛苦 撬在你身 伤在我心\N{\fs100}Oh. Oh, that's causing me pain. It hurts me more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.40,0:25:16.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了\N{\fs100}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.44,0:25:22.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一定要启动啊\N{\fs100}Please start.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.16,0:25:27.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太好了 给足了你空气\N{\fs100}Yes. And I've given you air.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:34.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}还有一件事我可以做 帮助冷却发动机\N{\fs100}There was one other thing I could do to help cool the engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.88,0:25:37.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但其痛苦程度难以想象\N{\fs100}but it was unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.88,0:25:40.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不想这样做 但我不得不\N{\fs100}I don't want to do it. I'm going to have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.56,0:25:41.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}把暖风调大\N{\fs100}Turn the heating up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.96,0:25:47.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为这样一来 会把发动机舱下的热空气吸出来\N{\fs100}because that will actually pull hot air out from under the engine bay
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:49.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}送到我这里\N{\fs100}and deliver it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:52.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在热起来了\N{\fs100}Oh, yeah, that is hot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.48,0:25:59.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}镜头转向前方\N{\fs100}Up ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.96,0:26:04.32,顶端1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这里指Top Gear北极特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.96,0:26:04.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}上一次如此孤独 还是和詹姆斯在北极\N{\fs100}I hadn't felt this alone since James and I drove to the North Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.48,0:26:11.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}毛里塔尼亚空无一人\N{\fs100}Mauritania is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.96,0:26:14.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}入眼之处 尽是荒芜\N{\fs100}Totally empty. Look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.04,0:26:19.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}荒无人烟\N{\fs100}No one comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.40,0:26:26.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当我们拿到拍摄许可证时 许可证编号是58\N{\fs100}When we got the filming permit, it was number 58.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:28.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是毛里塔尼亚自1960年以来\N{\fs100}The 58th filming permit
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.28,0:26:32.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}签发的第58张拍摄许可证\N{\fs100}this country has issued since 1960.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:36.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那可是63年啊\N{\fs100}That's 63 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:39.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这么长时间 只签发了58张拍摄许可证\N{\fs100}They've only issued 58 filming permits.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.12,0:26:49.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}哈蒙德 你回来了\N{\fs100}Hammond, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:52.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在引擎盖上打了孔 开着暖风在跑\N{\fs100}Made holes in the bonnet and I'm running with the heater on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.72,0:26:54.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我命不久矣\N{\fs100}I don't have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:57.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那可不怎么样\N{\fs100}Ooh, I don't fancy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.12,0:27:06.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们带着"自热锅"同事继续前行\N{\fs100}We continued onwards with our boil-in-the-bag colleague
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.48,0:27:09.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}直到三台口渴的引擎需要加油\N{\fs100}until our thirsty engines needed petrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.60,0:27:14.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}由于撒哈拉没多少加油站\N{\fs100}Which, because the Sahara doesn't have many service stations,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.68,0:27:19.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们只能靠威尔曼先生提供的加油车了\N{\fs100}meant pulling over at a fuel bowser that Mr Wilman had provided.
