Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.68,0:34:15.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果上边写的是 "小心 毛毛虫出没"\N{\fs100}If it said "Caution caterpillars",
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.64,0:34:16.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我会想进去看看\N{\fs100}I'd go and have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:20.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但是 只挂标识不埋雷 不也一样 吗\N{\fs100}But, I mean, you only need to put the sign up, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.44,0:34:23.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 但也有可能真就埋雷了\N{\fs100}Yeah, but you might have put the mines in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.64,0:34:27.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 但换做是我 我肯定只挂个标识\N{\fs100}Yeah, but if I were them, I'd just put the sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:31.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-那是因为你很懒而且没有地雷 -是的\N{\fs100}-You're lazy and don't have any mines. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.32,0:34:37.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我认为 那里没有地雷\N{\fs100}No, but in my mind, there aren't any mines there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我们要进去慢跑一圈吗 -算了\N{\fs100}-Shall we go for a little jog? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.80,0:34:43.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是什么...\N{\fs100}What the hell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.16,0:34:47.78,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-那是什么 -雷区\N{\fs100}-What's that? -It's a minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.78,0:34:49.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是的 -哈蒙德刚刚进去过了\N{\fs100}-A minefield. -Hammond's been in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.84,0:34:52.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你进去过了吗 -他冲破了栅栏\N{\fs100}-You've been in it? -He crashed through the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:56.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们现在遇到了问题\N{\fs100}We now had a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:35:02.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}横在我们面前的 是一个必须假定为真的雷区\N{\fs100}In front of us was what we had to assume was an actual minefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.56,0:35:06.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}挡在我们后面的 是一条充斥着有毒蝙蝠粪便的隧道\N{\fs100}While behind us was a tunnel full of infected bat dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.76,0:35:13.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不想重新回去穿过埃博拉隧道\N{\fs100}I don't want to go back through the tunnel of Ebola.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.08,0:35:15.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且即便我们原路返回\N{\fs100}And even if we do go back that way
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.08,0:35:17.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}还有那巨大的悬崖\N{\fs100}here's that massive cliff face.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.28,0:35:20.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 但那是个可以尝试克服的问题\N{\fs100}Yes, but that's a problem to try and overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是可以尝试解决的问题\N{\fs100}That's something to try and solve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.32,0:35:24.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而这不行 根本无法解决\N{\fs100}-That isn't. You can't solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.08,0:35:25.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 所以我们别无选择\N{\fs100}-Yes, so, we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.60,0:35:28.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-应该朝那边走 -你说得对 相当对\N{\fs100}-That's navigation. -You're right. You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.32,0:35:30.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们别无...我们不能...\N{\fs100}We have no... We cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.80,0:35:32.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有雷!\N{\fs100}Not in the minefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.96,0:35:35.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}停车\N{\fs100}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.84,0:35:38.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-停车 -停车\N{\fs100}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.44,0:35:43.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}威尔曼的预告片可能有戏了\N{\fs100}Wilman might get his trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.12,0:35:45.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}卡车爆炸的时候 你们要站在这儿不动吗\N{\fs100}No, well, are you gonna stand here while he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.28,0:35:46.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不 我要后退\N{\fs100}No, I'm gonna back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.52,0:35:52.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}油罐车消失在了视线中 但并没有爆炸\N{\fs100}The fuel tanker disappeared out of sight without detonating.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.12,0:35:54.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但这并没有改变我们的想法\N{\fs100}But that didn't change our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.64,0:35:59.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}于是我们调转方向...\N{\fs100}So, we turned round...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:03.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}顺着隧道原路返回\N{\fs100}...and went back through the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.32,0:36:08.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们怎么越过悬崖\N{\fs100}How are we going to get over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.56,0:36:11.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不知道怎么才能越过\N{\fs100}I don't know how we're going to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:23.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}数小时之后 我们终于找到了一条\N{\fs100}After many hours, we eventually found a rough track,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.32,0:36:27.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看起来可能通向悬崖顶部的崎岖小路\N{\fs100}which looked like it might go to the top of the escarpment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.84,0:36:31.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这一段有点坎坷\N{\fs100}Ooh, this is bumpy, this bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:37.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好样的 加油啊 捷豹 你可以的\N{\fs100}Yeah. Come on, Jag. You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.08,0:36:42.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这辆车让我大为惊讶\N{\fs100}This car is actually surprising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.84,0:36:45.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得可能是因为 这辆捷豹很轻 不是吗\N{\fs100}I suppose it's 'cause it's light, isn't it, the Jag?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:48.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是啊 重量会很大程度上影响性能\N{\fs100}Well, that makes a huge difference, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.84,0:36:51.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得我这辆车现在有两吨多了\N{\fs100}I think mine probably weighs more than two tonnes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.60,0:36:55.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}加油啊\N{\fs100}Come on. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.12,0:37:04.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}该死\N{\fs100}Oh, bloody hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.32,0:37:11.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 加油啊\N{\fs100}God, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.08,0:37:14.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}完蛋玩意儿\N{\fs100}Bollocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:18.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他来了 他开着捷豹来了\N{\fs100}Here he comes, in the Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.76,0:37:20.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你会撞到那块大石头的\N{\fs100}You're going to hit that big rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.64,0:37:21.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你瞧好了...\N{\fs100}-Behold the-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.64,0:37:21.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}Oooh.\N{\fs100}你瞧好了...\N{\fs100}-Behold the-
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:29.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}杰里米 如果你能轻轻推我一下 那就太好了\N{\fs100}If you can move and give me a tiny nudge, Jezza, that would be brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.16,0:37:39.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}小马拉了大车\N{\fs100}The gazelle has moved the walrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.84,0:37:41.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}非常感谢\N{\fs100}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.08,0:37:47.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}加油啊 慢一点 就是这样\N{\fs100}Come on, gently. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.40,0:37:55.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有点爱上这辆捷豹了\N{\fs100}I'm beginning to rather like my Jaag.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.64,0:38:00.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}实在抱歉 我最开始对这辆车很失望\N{\fs100}I'm sorry I was initially disappointed in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.04,0:38:02.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但现在我觉得它太棒了\N{\fs100}Because it's bloody brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.32,0:38:07.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}最终 我们实现了目标\N{\fs100}Eventually, we achieved our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.92,0:38:13.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这绝对是最高处...\N{\fs100}Well, this is definitely the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.92,0:38:17.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要我说\N{\fs100}I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.56,0:38:23.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那里看起来好像是一个建筑工地\N{\fs100}And that appears to be a... that's a building site.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.16,0:38:25.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那是我们的加油车吗\N{\fs100}Is that our fuel bowser?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.76,0:38:29.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它肯定穿过雷区了 不是吗\N{\fs100}He must have got through that minefield, mustn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.48,0:38:33.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它还没爆炸 威尔曼先生肯定会非常生气\N{\fs100}Mr Wilman's going to be furious 'cause it hasn't blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.40,0:38:35.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他的预告片没戏了\N{\fs100}He's got nothing for his trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.16,0:38:39.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 伙计们 我想就此停车\N{\fs100}Yeah, uh, chaps, I'm inclined to stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.96,0:38:41.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}为什么\N{\fs100}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:43.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们自己看\N{\fs100}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.40,0:38:48.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看 那里有一条路\N{\fs100}Ooh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:51.90,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-还真是啊 -是的 还是条好路\N{\fs100}Well, yeah, there is, and it is a nice road, but
