Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:58.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-但那条马路连不到这里吧 -没错 不连着\N{\fs100}It doesn't join up with here, does it? It's not connected to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.16,0:39:04.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我们把车从这里开下去 -什么\N{\fs100}-We'll drive down here. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:07.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我们把车从这里开下去 -"可不嘛 沿着那条路"\N{\fs100}Yeah, down that track.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.28,0:39:08.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这可是悬崖\N{\fs100}It's a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.36,0:39:11.26,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们站立的地方和那条路之间\N{\fs100}There's too much gravity immediately available
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.26,0:39:13.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可要受到不小的重力影响\N{\fs100}between where we're standing and that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.52,0:39:15.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但重力是安全可预测的\N{\fs100}And it isn't a cruel and unpredictable mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.48,0:39:16.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 非常可靠\N{\fs100}No, it's bloody reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.80,0:39:18.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}听我说 如果我先走\N{\fs100}-Listen, if I go first... -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.80,0:39:20.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-其实我已经准备好这么做了... -真的吗\N{\fs100}Which I'm prepared to do... -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.80,0:39:21.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的 我先走\N{\fs100}Yeah, I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.88,0:39:24.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-备用货车在那儿 对吧 -对\N{\fs100}The backup van's there, yes? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.44,0:39:26.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}备用车里肯定有线缆\N{\fs100}That's bound to have some cable in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.48,0:39:30.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}为啥不把我的车 跟一台挖掘机连在一起呢\N{\fs100}Why don't I attach my car to one of those diggers?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:33.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}其实 我们可以 把另一台挖掘机当做滑轮\N{\fs100}Actually, we could use the other one as a pulley.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.28,0:39:35.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后我开车下去\N{\fs100}And then I drive down,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.36,0:39:38.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我有线缆确保我的安全\N{\fs100}but I've got the safety of the cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.00,0:39:42.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你小时候肯定是把工程师和漫画家搞混淆了\N{\fs100}Years ago, at some point, you confused engineers with cartoonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:45.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你这样做是非常值得赞扬的\N{\fs100}What this is, is a very, very, very
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.16,0:39:48.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}经过精心设计的自杀行为\N{\fs100}commendably elaborate suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:54.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}尽管如此 我们别无选择\N{\fs100}Nevertheless, there was no other choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.36,0:39:57.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只能前往备用货车里翻箱倒柜\N{\fs100}so we went for a rummage in the backup van.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.64,0:40:01.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这条线缆很合适\N{\fs100}That is a proper cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:05.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}额定载重是四五吨\N{\fs100}Is it rated to four or five tonnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.08,0:40:06.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看起来是这样的\N{\fs100}Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.08,0:40:07.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}肯定会非常沉\N{\fs100}It'll be incredibly heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.48,0:40:08.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好的 准备好了吗 -小心脚\N{\fs100}-Right, are we ready? -Feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.88,0:40:10.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}开始了\N{\fs100}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.60,0:40:19.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在没求助挖掘机驾驶员的情况下 布置好了线缆\N{\fs100}Once I'd rigged up the cables with no help at all from the digger drivers,
