Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.68,0:40:25.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"一万乌吉亚\N{\fs100}Ten thousand MRU's.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.28,0:40:27.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"克拉克森勋爵"\N{\fs100}Lord Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.76,0:40:31.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}恐怕我没有支票保付卡\N{\fs100}I don't have a check guarantee card, I'm afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.12,0:40:33.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但放心吧 我可是有捷豹的人\N{\fs100}but it's OK, because I have a "Jaaaag".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.74,0:40:36.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后我向同事们解释了 整个装置的布置\N{\fs100}I then explained the setup to my colleagues.
