Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.60,0:41:03.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-他会说英语吗 -什么\N{\fs100}-Does he speak English? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.28,0:41:04.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-他会... -不会\N{\fs100}-Does he... -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.32,0:41:07.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们都是毛里塔尼亚人 但会说阿语和法语\N{\fs100}They're all actually Mauritanian, but they speak Arabic and French.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.64,0:41:09.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好的 -阿语没戏\N{\fs100}-Arabic? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.84,0:41:11.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-法语 -法语 全靠我了\N{\fs100}French? -French. I'm your man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.36,0:41:15.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}后盾搞定之后 我爬上了车\N{\fs100}With my back-up sorted, I climbed aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:18.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你要挂档下去还是空档下去\N{\fs100}Are you going to go down in gear or in neutral?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.64,0:41:22.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我得开车 不是吗我得挂一档\N{\fs100}I've got to drive, haven't I? I need to be in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.48,0:41:24.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 我们准备好了吗\N{\fs100}Right, are we ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.64,0:41:27.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}放心交给我们吧 我们会帮你看好的 我们支持你\N{\fs100}Stand on us, we'll see you right. You have our support.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.40,0:41:33.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.60,0:41:37.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-向左 -左一点点\N{\fs100}Little bit of left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:38.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}左一点点\N{\fs100}Bit of left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.84,0:41:42.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你很接近...你正在驶下悬崖\N{\fs100}You're very close to the... you're driving off a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.80,0:41:44.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我看不...但好处是\N{\fs100}But the good thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.80,0:41:47.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}由于我的Stratos聚光灯组 我看不到眼前\N{\fs100}due to my Stratos spotlights,, I can't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.56,0:41:56.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧\N{\fs100}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.96,0:42:03.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我才意识到我要怎么下去 并不喜欢这样\N{\fs100}I can now see what I've got to do for the first time. Don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.16,0:42:10.10,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}说实话 我真不喜欢这样\N{\fs100}Actually, really don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.36,0:42:16.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我得向左走\N{\fs100}I need to go left.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.16,0:42:21.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}麻烦让他把机械臂往左挥\N{\fs100}If you can ask him to swing his arm left.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.28,0:42:23.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}把机械臂往左挥 马上通知\N{\fs100}Swing his arm left. On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.04,0:42:25.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我可不想掉进那条沟壑里\N{\fs100}'Cause I don't want to go down that gully.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.08,0:42:29.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}（法语）请 非常\N{\fs100}S'il vous plaît, beaucoup...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:30.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}...左\N{\fs100}left.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.00,0:42:31.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}（法语）右\N{\fs100}Droite.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.36,0:42:37.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}哈蒙德 不管你刚才比划了啥 效果还不错\N{\fs100}Whatever you mimed, Hammond, wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.52,0:42:41.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}拜托 转向啊 你个混蛋\N{\fs100}Come on, turn, turn, turn, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.64,0:42:47.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好的 往左\N{\fs100}Come left, come left.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:49.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}往左啊 我的小山羊汽车\N{\fs100}Come left, my little mountain goat of a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.68,0:42:53.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这样好多了 -笔直向前\N{\fs100}-That's better. -All straightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.84,0:43:03.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 我在干什么\N{\fs100}Christ, what am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.52,0:43:15.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}到达这个位置之后 我认为剩下的路\N{\fs100}I'd now reached a point where I reckoned I could go the rest of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.04,0:43:16.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}完全可以靠我自己的动力\N{\fs100}under my own steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.36,0:43:22.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这不是很实用的日常解决方案吧\N{\fs100}It's not a practical, everyday kind of solution, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.00,0:43:24.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-速度不算快 -没错\N{\fs100}-It's not quick. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.28,0:43:26.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-而且还得准备几台挖掘机 -是啊\N{\fs100}-And you need a couple of spare diggers. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.08,0:43:29.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好的 我开始了\N{\fs100}OK, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.64,0:43:31.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 我的妈呀\N{\fs100}Ooh, God, struth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.92,0:43:33.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在侧着走\N{\fs100}I'm going sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.88,0:43:39.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}笔直向前\N{\fs100}Straighten out!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.20,0:43:46.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 速度和动力\N{\fs100}OK. Speed and power!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.32,0:43:58.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我上路了\N{\fs100}I'm on a road! I'm on a road!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.80,0:44:01.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}哈蒙德和梅 现在轮到你们了\N{\fs100}Hammond and May, your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.20,0:44:04.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的很简单 一点也不可怕\N{\fs100}It's really easy, not frightening at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.24,0:44:09.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但是 在我们与杰里米汇合之前\N{\fs100}Before we could join Jeremy, though, we had to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.40,0:44:14.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们得先确保 珍贵的重达九吨的油罐车安全驶下悬崖\N{\fs100}that our precious nine-tonne fuel tanker got down safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.08,0:44:20.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果你必须将一辆油罐车驶下悬崖\N{\fs100}If you had to lower a fuel tanker down a cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.04,0:44:24.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那么在他们两人中 你最不想让谁牵头\N{\fs100}which two human beings would you least like to be in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.60,0:44:28.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们是百分之一百万的确定\N{\fs100}Are we one million percent sure
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.20,0:44:33.10,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这样做是安全的吗 -说实话 到不了百分之一百万\N{\fs100}this is going to be safe? Not a million percent, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.52,0:44:36.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}即便杰里米坐在那辆捷豹里 也没这辆油罐车重\N{\fs100}This is heavier than the Jag, though, even with him in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.04,0:44:40.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 送油罐车下去吧\N{\fs100}Right, send it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.56,0:44:52.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-不行 太多了 -太多了 回来 回来一点\N{\fs100}Too much. Back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.00,0:44:59.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}完球\N{\fs100}Ballocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.76,0:45:00.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}Oh dear
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.56,0:45:12.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这声音太可怕了\N{\fs100}That noise is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.64,0:45:26.30,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}路程过半后 司机请求释放线缆\N{\fs100}At the halfway point, the driver asked us to release the cables
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.30,0:45:29.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这样一来 剩余的下降路线 他可以靠自己来驾驶\N{\fs100}so he could do the rest of the drop on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.40,0:45:33.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 我知道油罐车里的那个人 是什么感觉\N{\fs100}OK, I know what it feels like for that man in that fuel tanker.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.20,0:45:37.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}菊花一紧\N{\fs100}Bottom loosening.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.24,0:45:40.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们必须尽力向左打方向 \N{\fs100}I think we need a bit of serious left-hand down
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.40,0:45:42.22,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}才能避免杰里米刚才遇到的问题\N{\fs100}if he's going to avoid the problem that Jeremy had,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.22,0:45:43.54,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为他不能往那个方向走太多\N{\fs100}'cause he mustn't go too far that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:46.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他需要...尽快开始向左转\N{\fs100}He needs to start going left as soon as he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.92,0:45:50.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯 现在我们是第一次\N{\fs100}James, now that we've moved down the hill a bit further
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.88,0:45:53.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-往山下走了一点... -怎么了\N{\fs100}-for the first time. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.04,0:45:55.26,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你看到我看到的东西了吗在那边\N{\fs100}Have you seen what I've seen over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.56,0:46:11.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的天啊\N{\fs100}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.04,0:46:15.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不好了\N{\fs100}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.32,0:46:31.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}先生们 加油车下山了\N{\fs100}Gentlemen, the fuel bowser is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.44,0:46:35.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}虽说卡住了 但确实下来了\N{\fs100}It's stuck, but it's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.96,0:46:39.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}兄弟们 好消息\N{\fs100}Guys, good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.44,0:46:43.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它很接近山脚下了 而且好消息是不会爆炸\N{\fs100}He's made it just about to the bottom. It's not going to blow up, which is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.12,0:46:45.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且前保险杠掉落\N{\fs100}And the front bumper has come off,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.52,0:46:49.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得这一幕放在预告片里 会非常好看\N{\fs100}which I think's going to work quite well as something in the trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.80,0:46:51.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}了不起\N{\fs100}That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.00,0:46:54.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的...太叹为观止了\N{\fs100}It is really really... That was proper impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.04,0:46:59.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}另一个境界 而且没爆炸 一点都没\N{\fs100}Something else. But, I mean, it's just... And it's no explosion, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.52,0:47:03.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你们怎么下来的 -我们顺着路开下来的\N{\fs100}-How did you get down? -Oh, we came on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.64,0:47:06.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你是说... -没错\N{\fs100}Are you telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.16,0:47:08.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}说实话 实在太意外了 路就在施工场地后边\N{\fs100}I'm not going to lie. It was quite a surprise. It's behind the building site.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.72,0:47:11.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们是在修路 所以有挖掘机\N{\fs100}That's why they've got those diggers and things over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.56,0:47:14.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-他们一直在修路 -但他们修完了 一路修到了顶部\N{\fs100}-They've been building a road. -They've just got to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.96,0:47:16.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-修的很平整 -很不错\N{\fs100}-It's a nice road. -It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.64,0:47:19.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-人齐了 大家都很高兴 很安全 -我不高兴\N{\fs100}We're all here. Everybody's happy. -I'm not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.20,0:47:20.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所有的车都下来了\N{\fs100}All the cars came down
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.28,0:47:22.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我坐着这个从那里下来的 那里 -是的\N{\fs100}I came down there. I came down that, in that. Yes, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.64,0:47:24.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}说实话 我们刚才很轻松 是一条新修的公路\N{\fs100}That was pretty easy. It's a new road.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.64,0:47:28.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很漂亮 是沥青路面 边缘还有一点沙子\N{\fs100}It's lovely. Fresh tarmac, a little sand on the very edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.84,0:47:35.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随着夕阳西下 以及车轮下的沥青路面\N{\fs100}With the sun setting and tarmac beneath our wheels,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.16,0:47:39.98,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们决定在天黑之前尽可能多赶赶路\N{\fs100}we decided to knock off as many miles as possible before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.88,0:47:52.78,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在白天的时候天气像蒸笼一样 但现在...\N{\fs100}I'll admit that in the day, it is a bit toasty warm, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.68,0:47:55.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}刚刚过了七点\N{\fs100}It's just gone seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.28,0:47:57.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}刚刚日落西山\N{\fs100}The sun has just gone down behind the hill there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:48:03.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}温度只有38度 太令人高兴了\N{\fs100}This is absolutely delightful. A mere 38 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.04,0:48:10.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}夜幕降临 我们把车停在路边安营扎寨\N{\fs100}As night fell, we pulled off the road to make camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:15.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯和我认为威尔曼先生 肯定在后备货车里放了一些豪华帐篷\N{\fs100}with James and I assuming Mr Wilman had put some luxury tents in the backup van.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.52,0:48:22.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我正在努力回忆 我以前有没有像今晚这样烦躁过\N{\fs100}I'm trying to remember if I've ever been as irritated as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.48,0:48:25.66,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太简陋了\N{\fs100}It's pretty poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.66,0:48:28.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这...就这破条件 哪怕是童子军也会拒绝的\N{\fs100}This is... Even a boy scout would say no to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.94,0:48:30.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这些帐篷他是从哪弄的\N{\fs100}Where's he got them from?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.52,0:48:34.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他是不是在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节结束后随手拿的\N{\fs100}Did he go to Glastonbury the day after it finished and just helped himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.36,0:48:37.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我不能...我有...我已经63岁了\N{\fs100}But I can't... I mean, I'm 63 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.08,0:48:40.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我连我的膝盖都碰不到 更别说脚指了\N{\fs100}I can barely touch my knees, leave alone my toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.60,0:48:43.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就这帐篷我早上起来怎么穿衣服\N{\fs100}How does he think I'm going to get dressed in that in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.20,0:48:46.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你知道什么让我更烦躁吗\N{\fs100}And do you know what's doubly irritating?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.48,0:48:47.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不知道 你说吧\N{\fs100}No, but go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.80,0:48:50.54,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-哈蒙德的帐篷好多了 -好太多了\N{\fs100}-Hammond's tent is better. -It's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.54,0:48:52.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}明知道六米开外的哈蒙德\N{\fs100}I'm never going to be able to get to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.16,0:48:55.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}睡得比我舒服 这让我怎么睡得着\N{\fs100}knowing that Hammond is having a better time 20 feet away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.84,0:48:59.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不想要这样的帐篷\N{\fs100}I do not need a tent like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.00,0:49:01.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}咱先不说其他 这帐篷是半透明的\N{\fs100}It's translucent apart from anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.96,0:49:05.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}威尔曼先生是不是走进商店里说 "哪个帐篷最便宜"\N{\fs100}Did he go into a shop and say, "What is the cheapest tent?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.16,0:49:07.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"哪个帐篷最便宜"\N{\fs100}"What is the cheapest tent?"
