Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.20,0:51:46.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这座欣盖提小镇 一千年前 真的是一千年前\N{\fs100}This town, Chinguetti, a thousand years ago, and I do mean a thousand years ago,
