Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.28,0:52:53.74,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这是油还是水 还是油水 沙质油水 -都不是\N{\fs100}Is it oil or water? Or oily water? -Sandy, oily water? -It's neither.
