Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:18.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嘿 听我说\N{\fs100}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.88,0:53:20.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我想在小镇上转一转 -好的\N{\fs100}I wanna look round this town. -Yes.
