Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.04,0:53:48.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我想四处看看这个历史遗址的原因\N{\fs100}The reason why I wanted to look around this historical site
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.72,0:53:51.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是因为很快 它就将不复存在\N{\fs100}is because soon, it won't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.72,0:53:58.97,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}撒哈拉沙漠正在...吞噬这座小镇\N{\fs100}The desert is... eating the town.
