Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.64,0:54:06.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 快看这个\N{\fs100}Bloody hell. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.00,0:54:10.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他肯定不会再修剪草坪了 对吧\N{\fs100}He's not gonna be mowing his lawn anymore, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.96,0:54:13.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 深达好几十厘米 甚至是几米\N{\fs100}So it's feet deep, metres deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.52,0:54:16.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-沙漠为什么要吞噬一座小镇 -快看那个\N{\fs100}-Why is the desert eating the town? -Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.32,0:54:19.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是这样的 如今有件事叫作全球变暖\N{\fs100}Well now, there's a thing called global warming.
