Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.96,0:54:31.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 意思就是 风吹动沙子\N{\fs100}So this is what, wind moving the sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.12,0:54:34.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是...植被逐渐死亡 演变成为沙漠\N{\fs100}Yes, it's just-Well, the vegetation is dying and becoming desert.
