Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.08,0:54:58.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你会很喜欢的\N{\fs100}You're gonna like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.76,0:55:02.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}与此同时 在其中一间图书馆里\N{\fs100}Meanwhile, in one of the libraries,
