Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.16,0:56:19.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}船长终于出现在阳光下\N{\fs100}James finally emerged into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.36,0:56:22.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嘿 怎么样好玩吗\N{\fs100}Hey, how are you doing? Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.44,0:56:23.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好玩 真的是棒极了\N{\fs100}Yeah, it was bloody fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.24,0:56:26.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有很多书 但有一本古老的书\N{\fs100}Lots of books but this ancient one
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.08,0:56:28.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}上边有关于先知生活的图解\N{\fs100}with diagrams in about lives of the prophets,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.00,0:56:29.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}每一个都有插图\N{\fs100}and every one was an illustration, like a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.80,0:56:31.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-像画一样 -他马上就要变脸了\N{\fs100}His mood is about to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.32,0:56:33.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们干了什么好事\N{\fs100}What have you done? What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.40,0:56:35.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你们干了什么好事 -我们一直在到处闲逛\N{\fs100}Well we've been hanging around. We've walked about,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.48,0:56:37.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们四处走走 看了看这座小镇\N{\fs100}looked at the town, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.72,0:56:39.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-哦 你说这个啊 -你发现了 是啊\N{\fs100}-You've noticed. -Oh that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.56,0:56:42.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-不是我们干的 -没错\N{\fs100}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.04,0:56:44.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这是... -我们刚参观完镇上的另一侧\N{\fs100}We got back from looking round this other bit of the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.40,0:56:47.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-回来后就看到了这个场景 -是的 没错\N{\fs100}-Yes. -...and found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.00,0:56:49.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你听说过尘魔\N{\fs100}You've heard of dust devils,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.32,0:56:51.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-有点像旋转的风 -是的\N{\fs100}those little like spinning winds? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.08,0:56:53.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你停车的位置 正处于这些街道的交叉口\N{\fs100}Where you parked, at this intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.40,0:56:56.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好的 -我认为由此可能增大了风力\N{\fs100}I think it maybe amplified the effect of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.24,0:56:59.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}导致风把沙子卷起来 全都堆在了你的车里\N{\fs100}and just picked it up and deposited it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.60,0:57:01.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是你们亲眼所见吗\N{\fs100}And you saw this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.76,0:57:04.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不 我们没看到 因为我们刚才在逛小镇的另一边\N{\fs100}No, we didn't, cos we were looking round the other town.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.36,0:57:06.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们还能想到一件事\N{\fs100}The only other thing we can think of,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.72,0:57:08.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我们已经绞尽脑汁了... -是的\N{\fs100}we've wracked our brains,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.32,0:57:10.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}...他们这里不开罚单\N{\fs100}is that they don't have tickets here,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.64,0:57:12.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}- 如果你把车停在路中间 -没错\N{\fs100}- if you park in the middle of the road. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.68,0:57:15.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}交通协管员就会用沙子填满你的车\N{\fs100}The traffic wardens simply fill your car with sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.12,0:57:17.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这理由真是...太妙了\N{\fs100}That's a-that's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.64,0:57:19.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但如果我的车坏了怎么办\N{\fs100}But what if my car doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.24,0:57:21.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-肯定没坏 -我怎样才能把沙子弄出来\N{\fs100}And how the hell do I get it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.64,0:57:24.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-钥匙在哪里 -你刚才放哪里了\N{\fs100}-Where's the key? -Ah. Where did you leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.08,0:57:25.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我放在中控台上了\N{\fs100}On the centre console, where I always leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.48,0:57:28.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-把车门打开 沙子就出来了 -车门锁上了\N{\fs100}If you just open the doors, the sand'll fall out. Well, it's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.16,0:57:30.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我从来不锁车\N{\fs100}You see, I never lock my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.44,0:57:32.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是防止这种情况的发生\N{\fs100}Just in case this exact thing happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.92,0:57:35.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 给我一把铲子 我把沙子铲出来 你们...\N{\fs100}OK, give me a shovel, I'll get it. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.52,0:57:37.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们就滚蛋吧\N{\fs100}Oh, bugger off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.44,0:57:43.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}留下船长去解决 他那怪异的沙尘问题之后\N{\fs100}Having left James to sort out his freak sandstorm issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.44,0:57:45.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们找到了后援货车\N{\fs100}we headed for the backup van,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.56,0:57:48.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为我们决定解决\N{\fs100}because we'd decided to solve the problems
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.28,0:57:52.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可怕的搓衣板路带来的一系列问题\N{\fs100}caused by the horrendous washboard roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.64,0:57:57.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊这是...\N{\fs100}Oh God, it's a, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.80,0:58:02.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}烫死了\N{\fs100}Oh, burning, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.16,0:58:07.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}谢谢\N{\fs100}Ah! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.88,0:58:11.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果想焊接...\N{\fs100}If you wanna do any welding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.64,0:58:14.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-或电锯 -或者角色扮演\N{\fs100}Or chainsawing. Or role play.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.44,0:58:17.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}稍等一下\N{\fs100}Now hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.56,0:58:19.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我可以用这些做点什么\N{\fs100}I could do something with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.04,0:58:21.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 我可以\N{\fs100}Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.60,0:58:27.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当船长努力清空他的车时...\N{\fs100}While James toiled away emptying his car...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.44,0:58:30.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真愚蠢\N{\fs100}Oh, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.80,0:58:34.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们忙于研究在货车里发现的东西\N{\fs100}...we got busy with what we'd found in the van,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.80,0:58:39.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很快 我们用来应对搓衣板路的改装方案准备就绪\N{\fs100}and soon our washboard solution modifications were ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.12,0:58:43.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在货车里找到了这个\N{\fs100}-So I found this in the truck. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.76,0:58:45.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这是一台耕耘机 -是的 没错\N{\fs100}-It's a cultivator. -It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.64,0:58:49.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可能会起作用 但是通常情况下\N{\fs100}It might work, but normally
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.32,0:58:53.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}耕耘机是拖在拖拉机后面的\N{\fs100}cultivators are towed behind the tractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.00,0:58:54.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}对 但那样的话 我得先开车走过崎岖路面\N{\fs100}Yes, but I'd have to drive over the rough road
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.92,0:58:56.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后耕耘机把我身后的路铺平\N{\fs100}before cultivating it level.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.80,0:58:57.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这样行不通\N{\fs100}That wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.92,0:58:59.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但这样做可以造福别人啊\N{\fs100}No, it would be more sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.80,0:59:00.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不想\N{\fs100}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.88,0:59:02.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你不想造福别人 -没错\N{\fs100}-You're not what, sociable? -Sociable.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.64,0:59:05.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我只想让自己舒服一点 让我的日子好过一点\N{\fs100}I want this for me to work and make my life better.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.64,0:59:07.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我觉得你会认为\N{\fs100}But I think you'll find my solution
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.48,0:59:11.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的改装方案比你这个优秀几百万倍\N{\fs100}surpasses this by a factor of several million.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.60,0:59:17.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我真不知道威尔曼先生 为什么明知我们要来撒哈拉沙漠\N{\fs100}I've literally no idea why Mr Wilman put two snowmobiles in the van,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.60,0:59:20.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}还要把两辆雪地摩托放进货车里 但我很高兴他这样做了\N{\fs100}knowing we're going to the Sahara Desert, but I'm glad he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.12,0:59:24.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}容我解释一下 好吗\N{\fs100}Let me explain. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.08,0:59:26.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我没用滑雪板 而是在前面装了轮子\N{\fs100}Instead of using the skis, I've fitted wheels at the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.40,0:59:29.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但轮子并不是让我们感兴趣的部分\N{\fs100}but we're not really interested in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.28,0:59:32.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们感兴趣的是这些履带\N{\fs100}What we are interested in is the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.48,0:59:36.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它们将在我的车轮前呼啸而过\N{\fs100}They're gonna be whizzing along in front of my wheels,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.52,0:59:38.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}抚平搓衣板路面上的\N{\fs100}smoothing out the ridges
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.48,0:59:41.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}各种凸起\N{\fs100}in the washboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.84,0:59:43.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 当我驶过后\N{\fs100}So when I arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.56,0:59:45.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}路面会变得难以置信的光滑 就像一张台球桌\N{\fs100}incredibly smooth, it'll be like a billiard table.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.28,0:59:49.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且它们会像 两个巨大的带式砂光机一样运转\N{\fs100}They're gonna be going eeeee, like two massive belt sanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.52,0:59:52.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 非常正确 它们就是带式砂光机\N{\fs100}Yes. Exactly right, they're belt sanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.32,0:59:55.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}安装在捷豹F-Type的前部\N{\fs100}mounted to the front of a Jaguar F-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.36,0:59:59.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是的 -越野捷豹...越野F型\N{\fs100}-Yeah. -Off road Jag. An F-Off roader type.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.12,1:00:03.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很不可思议吧与其被关在一个 单调乏味的精神病院单间\N{\fs100}It's incredible, isn't it? Rather than be locked up in a drab cell,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.08,1:00:05.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}穿着背后系扣的病号服\N{\fs100}in a jacket that does up at the back,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.20,1:00:09.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不如有这么多机会 让你的疯狂点子变为现实\N{\fs100}you've had so many opportunities to make your insanity real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.56,1:00:10.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}成果就在眼前\N{\fs100}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.80,1:00:14.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随着技术简报会结束\N{\fs100}With the technical briefings over,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.64,1:00:18.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是时候将理论付诸实践了\N{\fs100}it was time to put theory into practice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.92,1:00:20.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}抬升设备\N{\fs100}Raising rig.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.88,1:00:25.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}理查德哈蒙德 驶向未来\N{\fs100}Richard Hammond. To the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.52,1:00:39.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我猜这座小镇上的大多数人\N{\fs100}I'm guessing that most of the people in this town
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.00,1:00:42.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}都还没见过雪地摩托\N{\fs100}have not yet seen a snowmobile.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.72,1:00:46.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等他们听说了雪地摩托的用途后 肯定会感到非常惊讶\N{\fs100}They're going to be quite surprised to hear what its primary purpose is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.88,1:00:50.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显然 我现在把它放在高位\N{\fs100}Obviously, I have it in a raised position right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.12,1:00:51.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我可以通过液压降低它的高度\N{\fs100}I can hydraulically lower it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.84,1:00:54.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就像007的那台路特斯\N{\fs100}It's just like James Bond's Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.16,1:00:56.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在普通模式下 这就是一辆普通的汽车\N{\fs100}In normal car mode, it's just a normal car.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.04,1:01:04.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}来到城外的搓衣板路面之后\N{\fs100}Once we came to a washboard section of road outside the town,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.64,1:01:08.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们为首次测试做好了准备\N{\fs100}we prepared for our maiden trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.08,1:01:15.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}雪地摩托开始运转\N{\fs100}Snowmobiles are running.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.68,1:01:18.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 我要开始了\N{\fs100}Right, I'm doing it. I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.76,1:01:23.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}开始 正在降低高度\N{\fs100}Here we go. Lowering.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.92,1:01:31.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们开始\N{\fs100}And here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.12,1:01:38.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 我觉得它起作用了\N{\fs100}By Jove, I think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.64,1:01:42.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不...真的\N{\fs100}I mean I... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.40,1:01:46.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我正在雕刻道路 正在抚平道路\N{\fs100}I am sculpting the roads. I'm smoothing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.96,1:01:51.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我正在平整道路\N{\fs100}I am grading the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.56,1:01:53.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}God!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:56.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真不敢相信眼前的一切\N{\fs100}Cannot believe that this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.64,1:02:15.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太棒了\N{\fs100}Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.52,1:02:18.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而我就坐在这里尽情放松\N{\fs100}And I'll just sit here now and relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.68,1:02:21.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要记住 受益人不只我一个\N{\fs100}And it's not just me that's benefitting. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.84,1:02:24.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}整个非洲都会由此受益\N{\fs100}The whole of Africa is benefitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.88,1:02:30.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}石头被弹起来了 快看 耕耘机弹起了很多石头\N{\fs100}Oh, stones are coming. See, it's kicking up some stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.24,1:02:34.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 会有这种情况发生\N{\fs100}Oh yeah, that can happen. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.80,1:02:36.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 有几块大石头\N{\fs100}Oh yeah, that's some big stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.48,1:02:41.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但尽管存在这个小问题\N{\fs100}But despite this teething problem,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.84,1:02:45.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当我们在几公里后靠边停车 检查作业情况时\N{\fs100}when we pulled over a few miles later to inspect our work,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.80,1:02:49.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}结果是毫无疑问的\N{\fs100}the results were unquestionable.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.84,1:02:52.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看看左手边的道路\N{\fs100}You look on the left-hand side of the road, which is what we have graded,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.80,1:02:55.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也就是我们平整过的那一侧\N{\fs100}that side,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.44,1:03:00.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后再看看右手边 也就是我们没有平整过的一侧\N{\fs100}and then look at the right-hand side of the road, which we haven't graded,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.32,1:03:03.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这就是...证据 -起作用了\N{\fs100}-I mean it... proof. -It works, it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.44,1:03:07.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这条路上简直都能跑F1了 -太简单了\N{\fs100}-You could run an F1 race on that. -Oh, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.76,1:03:11.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随后我们决定满怀公益精神\N{\fs100}We then decided to be fully public spirited,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.68,1:03:16.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}齐头并进 这样就能把所有路面全都抚平\N{\fs100}and drive side by side, so we could smooth out all of the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.72,1:03:20.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 哈蒙德 我们出发吧\N{\fs100}OK, Hammond, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.36,1:03:23.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们可以同时平整两条车道\N{\fs100}We could do dual carriageways.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.60,1:03:26.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我感觉我可以更深一些\N{\fs100}I reckon I can go a bit deeper here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.04,1:03:29.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是要...我正在学习 如何巧妙地运用这个系统\N{\fs100}Just gotta... I'm learning to finesse the system now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.68,1:03:33.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}糟糕\N{\fs100}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.76,1:03:41.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不好了\N{\fs100}Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.44,1:03:43.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的天啊\N{\fs100}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.52,1:03:51.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我从来没有见过这样的事情\N{\fs100}I've never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.24,1:03:55.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我看到了一股烟 然后雪地摩托就开走了 然后...\N{\fs100}I just saw a puff of smoke and it leapt that thing and...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.56,1:04:00.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但至少没有目击者 除了这辆卡车上的人之外\N{\fs100}At least there are no witnesses. Apart from the people in this lorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.80,1:04:07.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我现在要静静地开过去 -是啊\N{\fs100}-I'm just gonna quietly move along. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.76,1:04:09.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了\N{\fs100}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.36,1:04:13.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只要我跟你一起走 人们就不会发现少了一台雪地摩托\N{\fs100}If I drive alongside, people won't spot that there's one missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.32,1:04:15.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 好主意 哈蒙德\N{\fs100}Yeah, good thinking Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.64,1:04:19.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}刚才那场景也太独特了 我也很有信心\N{\fs100}Well, that was unique. I'm pretty confident...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.68,1:04:24.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得耕耘机坏了\N{\fs100}Oh, I think it just broke.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.36,1:04:30.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在第二次事故后 我们决定\N{\fs100}After this second incident, we decided to abandon all road mending
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.56,1:04:33.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}放弃眼下所有的道路修补工作\N{\fs100}for the foreseeable future.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.76,1:04:40.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}起初 我们的实验结果非常出色\N{\fs100}Initially, our experiment was brilliant, and then everything went
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.20,1:04:43.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}后来局面变得非常糟糕 急转直下\N{\fs100}terribly, badly wrong...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.48,1:04:45.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的是急转直下\N{\fs100}very quickly indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.16,1:04:47.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你准备演讲稿了吗 我准备了\N{\fs100}Had you prepared speeches? I had.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.40,1:04:50.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我之前不知道自己会得 司令勋章还是官佐勋章\N{\fs100}I didn't know whether I'd get a CBE or an OBE.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.76,1:04:53.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我本来指望人们为我立一尊雕像 然后请我去TED演讲\N{\fs100}I was gonna get a statue and do a TED talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.24,1:04:56.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}恐怕现在两个我都得不到了\N{\fs100}I'm probably not gonna get either now,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.12,1:04:59.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}特别是考虑到我的雪地摩托 可能撞进了了一座偏远的村庄\N{\fs100}particularly if my snowmobile crashes into a remote village.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.60,1:05:03.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们觉得船长最后肯定会赶上来\N{\fs100}Assuming May would eventually catch up,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.40,1:05:05.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以决定先行一步\N{\fs100}we decided to press on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.24,1:05:12.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但是 随着夜幕降临 我的马丁再次开始作妖\N{\fs100}But, as darkness fell, my Aston began to play up. Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.00,1:05:16.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我又过热了\N{\fs100}Er, I'm just overheating again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.00,1:05:18.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车让我立即停车\N{\fs100}I've been told to stop immediately by the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.76,1:05:22.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我好像没法挂到三档以上 所以转速太高了\N{\fs100}I can't seem to get past third gear, so it's running at too high RPM.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.40,1:05:24.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 哈蒙德\N{\fs100}OK, Hammond. Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.24,1:05:28.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我真的一点儿忙也帮不上\N{\fs100}there's literally nothing I can do about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.08,1:05:32.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不会吧 太遗憾了 但你说得对\N{\fs100}No, that was a sigh, but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.24,1:05:37.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随着同事的尾灯消失在夜色中\N{\fs100}As my colleague's taillights dissolved into the night,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.08,1:05:40.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我独自一人继续前行\N{\fs100}I was left to trundle on... alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.16,1:05:48.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}已经很晚了 而且我的车速 不能超过每小时32公里\N{\fs100}Er, it's late and I can't go much more than 20 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.28,1:05:51.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}变速箱失灵了 没法升档\N{\fs100}The gearbox is failing. It won't shift up.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.24,1:05:52.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我卡在第二档了\N{\fs100}I'm stuck in second.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.96,1:05:56.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且只要我的转速超过 每分钟1500\N{\fs100}And if I run it any higher than one and a half thousand RPM,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.16,1:05:57.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}发动机就会过热\N{\fs100}the engine overheats.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.64,1:06:00.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}此外 我收到了车辆的警告\N{\fs100}Also I'm getting warnings telling me check battery off switch,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.16,1:06:05.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}让我检查电池 关闭开关 刹车故障 安全停车\N{\fs100}brake failure, stop safely and my dashboard lights have gone out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.12,1:06:08.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}仪表盘的灯也灭了 又亮了\N{\fs100}Oh, they've come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.04,1:06:10.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"急需保养SRS安全气囊\N{\fs100}SRS airbag service urgent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.92,1:06:14.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"翻车保护出现故障 需要进行DSC保养"\N{\fs100}Rollover protect fault. DSC service required.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.08,1:06:18.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}加油啊\N{\fs100}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.84,1:06:22.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}得带你去营地 稍微修理一下\N{\fs100}Gonna get you to camp. Bit of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.96,1:06:40.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}第二天早上 船长和我汇合了\N{\fs100}The next morning, James and I were reunited.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.52,1:06:42.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}Oh God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.72,1:06:52.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我尿完了\N{\fs100}Oh I'm empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.72,1:06:57.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-早上好 梅 -早上好\N{\fs100}-Morning, May. -Morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.04,1:07:03.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你知道画面里少了什么吗\N{\fs100}Have you seen what's missing from this picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.80,1:07:04.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}知道\N{\fs100}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.92,1:07:13.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在他俩后面 他们领先我几公里\N{\fs100}I am behind the other two. They're some miles ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.08,1:07:15.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我会赶上他们的\N{\fs100}I will find them,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.32,1:07:18.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我现在要把车修好 否则寸步难行\N{\fs100}but I can't go on any further, until I've sorted this car.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.56,1:07:20.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 我昨晚在这里小憩了一晚 因为我可以\N{\fs100}So I kipped here last night, cos I can,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.76,1:07:22.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}毕竟我有一家阿斯顿马丁酒店\N{\fs100}cos I've got an Aston Martin hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.80,1:07:24.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但这台阿斯顿马丁运转得不是很顺畅\N{\fs100}But the Aston Martin bit isn't working very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.28,1:07:27.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在的情况是 我出席了这款车的发布会\N{\fs100}I did the launch of this car.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.24,1:07:28.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我记得刚发布的时候\N{\fs100}I remember when they came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.76,1:07:32.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}恰恰是汽车开始变得更加智能的时刻\N{\fs100}It's from the exact point when cars started getting cleverer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.68,1:07:34.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但智能程度还不够\N{\fs100}But not clever enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.16,1:07:36.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}通常而言 汽车上所有的电子部件\N{\fs100}Normally everything on the car electric
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.12,1:07:37.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}都是通过独立的线路控制的\N{\fs100}was controlled by a separate wire,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.92,1:07:40.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这种情况下 如果你只有一个喇叭 那还可以接受\N{\fs100}which is OK when all you had was a horn.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.28,1:07:43.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但如今 所有部件 都是通过电子设备来操作的\N{\fs100}But by this time, everything was worked with electronics,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.40,1:07:47.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以他们把所有线路 合并成了一条巨大又智能的线路\N{\fs100}so they combined them all into one gigantic, very clever wire
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.20,1:07:49.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}绕着全车走 连接不同的零件\N{\fs100}that went all the way round the car and stopped off at all the different things.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.96,1:07:53.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}汽车可以感知到一切 比如刹车 悬挂系统\N{\fs100}And the car can feel everything, its brakes, its suspension,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.28,1:07:55.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这非常棒 但一旦感知不到的时候 就出问题了\N{\fs100}which is great, until it can't feel them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.28,1:08:00.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 如果车辆感觉不到变速箱了 就会停用变速箱\N{\fs100}So if it can't feel its gearbox, it stops using its gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.92,1:08:03.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这里面的某个地方有东西短路了\N{\fs100}Somewhere in there is one little thing that's just shorting across,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.60,1:08:06.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}导致整个中央神经系统陷入瘫痪\N{\fs100}and it's sending the whole of its central nervous system into meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.08,1:08:09.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}出问题的可能是这里任何一处\N{\fs100}And it could be anywhere in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.20,1:08:12.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而沙漠环境更是雪上加霜\N{\fs100}What's made it worse, is the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.76,1:08:15.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太烫了 到处都是石头和沙子\N{\fs100}It's hot. Full of stones and sand.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.12,1:08:16.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太烫了 需要冷却一下\N{\fs100}It's hot, so it needs cooling.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.36,1:08:19.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这前面是一个小小的散热器 一个很小的冷却器\N{\fs100}Here is a little radiator at the front, tiny little cooler.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.20,1:08:22.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是用来冷却变速箱的油 变速箱位于后部\N{\fs100}That cools oil for the gearbox, which is right at the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.56,1:08:25.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有一颗石头穿透了散热器 打了一个洞\N{\fs100}One of the stones has gone through the radiator, and made a hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.56,1:08:29.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}导致油漏了出来 溅到了散热器前侧\N{\fs100}That's allowed the oil to leak out and spread over the front of the radiator,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.08,1:08:32.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}再与沙子混合 相当于在它面前砌了一堵砖墙\N{\fs100}mingle with the sand and build a brick wall in front of itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.96,1:08:35.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因此 变速箱过热\N{\fs100}So the gearbox is overheating.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.00,1:08:38.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这个问题 我或许能做些什么 但对于电子部件\N{\fs100}That I could probably do something about, but as for the electronics,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.80,1:08:40.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我只能不断地寻找\N{\fs100}I'm just gonna have to look
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.36,1:08:43.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}直到我找到一个可以修复的故障\N{\fs100}until I can physically find a problem to mend.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.56,1:08:50.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}经过一个小时的调整后 我重新上路了\N{\fs100}After an hour of fettling, I got back on the road,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.52,1:08:54.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但这台马丁却完全没有修好\N{\fs100}but the Aston was by no means mended.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.60,1:08:58.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}车还在开 这是件好事 但我只有一档\N{\fs100}I'm moving, which is good. But I've only got one gear
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.44,1:09:02.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且我不知道 是发动机还是哪里出了什么故障\N{\fs100}and I've no idea what's happening to the engine or anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.12,1:09:04.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为我的仪表都不起作用 温度什么的 全都不显示了\N{\fs100}cos none of my gauges are working. Temperature, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.72,1:09:06.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以车子不让我换档\N{\fs100}That's why it's not letting me change gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.84,1:09:10.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}车子没有给我任何信息 因为它自己没有收到任何信息\N{\fs100}It's not giving me any information because it's not getting any information.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.64,1:09:12.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你好啊 加油车\N{\fs100}Oh, hello. The fuel bowser.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.32,1:09:16.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不知道我的车是不是还有油 但我还是加一点吧\N{\fs100}Well, I've no idea if I've got any fuel, but I'll get some anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.72,1:09:17.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的仪表不显示\N{\fs100}My gauge doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.32,1:09:20.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-看 -他来了\N{\fs100}-Oh, look. -Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.24,1:09:26.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你的车能动了 -是的 起码能动了\N{\fs100}-It's working! -Yes. More or less.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.08,1:09:30.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要让它休息一下\N{\fs100}I'm just gonna give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.60,1:09:32.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你有几个档位 -一个\N{\fs100}-How many gears have you got? -One.
