Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.56,1:17:29.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们就是在毁车\N{\fs100}We're just wrecking the cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.76,1:17:35.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}再坚持一下 翻过那座山\N{\fs100}For a bit more persevering we might just get over that crest there,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.56,1:17:36.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你就能看到了\N{\fs100}and there it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.28,1:17:48.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}完蛋\N{\fs100}Bollocks!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.88,1:17:51.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}见鬼\N{\fs100}Cock!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.88,1:17:54.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我陷车了 都怪你\N{\fs100}I'm stuck, and it's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.40,1:17:58.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所有那些从太空中能看到的景观\N{\fs100}All this stuff about seeing from outer space.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.56,1:18:00.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}比如中国的长城\N{\fs100}Think about the thing, the Great Wall of China,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.64,1:18:02.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"你可以从太空看到长城"\N{\fs100}famously "you can see that from out of space."
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.24,1:18:04.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在它旁边也应该能看到啊\N{\fs100}You can also see it when you're standing next to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.36,1:18:07.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}肯定在这儿 你就是不让我去找\N{\fs100}It is there. You just, you won't let me go and have a look for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.84,1:18:11.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也可能那只是某个老巫婆给你讲的童话故事\N{\fs100}Or it might have been a fairytale that Gypsy Rose told you,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.32,1:18:14.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为你给了她一点零钱\N{\fs100}because you'd given her £1.50.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.04,1:18:16.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧好吧 咱们不找了\N{\fs100}All right, all right, fine, well I'll-we'll give in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.32,1:18:18.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}虽然我不喜欢半途而废 但我放弃了\N{\fs100}I don't like giving in, but I'm going to give in.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.68,1:18:22.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}本来在非洲到处找一只眼睛这件事就很可笑\N{\fs100}Yeah, but you're giving in looking for something like an eye in the middle of Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.60,1:18:25.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-可她说过是一只巨大的眼睛 -有多大\N{\fs100}-Yes, it's a huge eye. -Huge, but how huge?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.56,1:18:29.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是...按照她的描述应该非常巨大\N{\fs100}Well, it's, the way she described it, like massive huge.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.32,1:18:32.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-对了 哈蒙德在哪里 -这是个好问题\N{\fs100}-Where's Hammond, by the way? -That is a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.24,1:18:34.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得他根本没心思来找非洲之眼\N{\fs100}I'm assuming he's not bothered to coming to look at the eye
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.88,1:18:37.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为他认为这是...\N{\fs100}cos he just thinks...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.64,1:18:48.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 我知道这个举动可能毫无意义 但是...\N{\fs100}OK, I know this is probably a pointless exercise, but let's...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.12,1:18:53.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}根本没有信号\N{\fs100}No signal at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.08,1:18:55.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}手机一点用也没有\N{\fs100}That is of no help.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.88,1:19:02.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没有大量液体流出\N{\fs100}There's no huge amounts of fluid that've come out,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.84,1:19:04.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但即使有也无法解释\N{\fs100}but even if they had, that wouldn't explain it just being
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.88,1:19:06.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}为什么无法启动\N{\fs100}dead at the key.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:07.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显然是电气系统的问题\N{\fs100}It's clearly electrics.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.36,1:19:13.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果这颗2005年的脆弱大脑坏死\N{\fs100}If its feeble 2005 brain has given up,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.00,1:19:14.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那我就完蛋了\N{\fs100}I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.56,1:19:17.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}唯一的另一种可能是电池\N{\fs100}The only other thing, battery.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.12,1:19:19.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}应该还有电对吧\N{\fs100}That's not gone flat has it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.60,1:19:21.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}电池在...\N{\fs100}But it's behind
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.16,1:19:24.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}座椅后边\N{\fs100}this seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.36,1:19:30.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}谢天谢地\N{\fs100}Oh dear Lord! Salvation!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.32,1:19:32.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等等 让我试一下\N{\fs100}No way. Hang on, let me just check.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.76,1:19:41.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}原来是电极松了\N{\fs100}The live battery terminal has shaken loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.36,1:19:46.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}应该是这一路的颠簸所致\N{\fs100}Literally this has shaken itself undone. It was like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.64,1:19:56.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我上路了 好消息接连不断\N{\fs100}I got going, and there was more good news,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.36,1:20:01.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的变速箱决定恪守本职\N{\fs100}because the gearbox had decided to actually be a gearbox again.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.68,1:20:05.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}阿斯顿马丁好样的\N{\fs100}Aston Martin! Yeah ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.36,1:20:09.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}档位什么的全都恢复了\N{\fs100}I've got gears, and everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.00,1:20:15.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}与此同时 在我们回到主干路的途中\N{\fs100}Meanwhile, on our way back to the main road,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.64,1:20:20.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我和梅被眼前的东西分散了注意力\N{\fs100}May and I had been rather distracted by something we had found.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.60,1:20:22.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}请看\N{\fs100}This.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.32,1:20:36.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 快看这个\N{\fs100}Bloody Nora, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.56,1:20:37.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}嘿 快看\N{\fs100}Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.68,1:20:53.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的老天爷啊\N{\fs100}Jesus wept!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.60,1:20:58.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是绿洲吗\N{\fs100}Is that an oasis?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.56,1:21:03.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没有证据能表明我是英国人\N{\fs100}Literally no evidence that I'm English.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.72,1:21:05.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等一下\N{\fs100}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.24,1:21:09.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}过来坐吧 我这里有应景的音乐\N{\fs100}Come and have a seat. I've got just the thing we should be listening to.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.32,1:21:12.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我找不到任何东西来纪念...\N{\fs100}I can't find anything to commemorate the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.76,1:21:15.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}理查德哈蒙德的去世\N{\fs100}demise of Richard Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.24,1:21:19.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你知道吗 戈登莱特福特也是今天去世的\N{\fs100}You know Gordon Lightfoot also died today. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.32,1:21:20.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是吗 -是的\N{\fs100}-Did he? -Yeah.
