Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.64,1:21:36.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ What a tale my thoughts could tell ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.44,1:21:41.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ Just like an old time movie ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.40,1:21:44.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ 'Bout a ghost from a wishing well ♪
