Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.20,1:21:53.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ With chains upon my feet ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.00,1:21:57.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ You know that ghost is me ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.20,1:22:01.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ And I will never be set free ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.00,1:22:06.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}♪ As long as I'm a ghost, you can't see ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.80,1:22:11.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我来告诉你们毛里塔尼亚有多空旷\N{\fs100}Just to give you an idea of how empty Mauritania is,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.28,1:22:15.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在这条贯穿整个国家的主干路上\N{\fs100}I've now done a hundred miles on this, the main road
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.92,1:22:17.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}跑了160公里\N{\fs100}from one side of the country to the other,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.44,1:22:22.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一辆车都没见到\N{\fs100}and I haven't seen another car, not one, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.28,1:22:26.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就是...让人头疼\N{\fs100}It's just... it hurts your head,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.88,1:22:29.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这个地方的广阔和空旷\N{\fs100}the bigness of this place, and the emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.44,1:22:37.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得前面有一辆被毁了容的阿斯顿马丁...\N{\fs100}I do believe it's a disfigured Aston Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.60,1:22:39.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 没错\N{\fs100}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.12,1:22:42.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}同事们追上了我\N{\fs100}My colleagues caught up with me
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.00,1:22:46.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而我这辆闹鬼的车又开始作妖了\N{\fs100}just as my haunted car started to play up... again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.92,1:22:50.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}变速箱再次失灵\N{\fs100}I've lost gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.12,1:22:53.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在开始哔哔作响了\N{\fs100}Oh, now it's beeping!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.04,1:23:02.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}车窗怎么打开了\N{\fs100}Why have my windows opened?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.04,1:23:04.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}怎么回事...我没动啊\N{\fs100}Why have my... who... I didn't ask them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.56,1:23:06.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车窗怎么打开了\N{\fs100}Why have my windows opened?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.56,1:23:09.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它现在不光不服从我 而且还折磨我\N{\fs100}It's actively disobeying and tormenting me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.08,1:23:12.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车自行决定打开车窗并剥夺我换档的能力\N{\fs100}It's, uh, decided to open the windows, and take away the ability to change gear,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.80,1:23:15.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}伴随着令人抓狂的哔哔声\N{\fs100}accompanied by a maddening beep.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.40,1:23:22.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我认为我的车之所以发出哔哔声\N{\fs100}I thought the beeping might be happening
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.04,1:23:26.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是因为它觉得我的车顶没有固定牢靠\N{\fs100}because the car didn't believe my roof was secured properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.72,1:23:29.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以我把车停在路边 验证我的猜想是否正确\N{\fs100}So, I pulled over to test my theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.52,1:23:35.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}混蛋\N{\fs100}Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.64,1:23:39.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}还在响\N{\fs100}It's still beeping!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.44,1:23:44.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这车的设计真是便捷 按一个按钮把车顶收起来\N{\fs100}It's got a very convenient roof, you just press the button, and it goes down,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.72,1:23:46.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后还得下车边跳边往下按\N{\fs100}and then you have to get out and jump on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.36,1:23:52.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我确实听说人在沙漠里待久了就会被逼疯\N{\fs100}They do say that people are driven mad in the desert after a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.08,1:23:57.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}试试中间这块\N{\fs100}What about in the middle? The bit in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.08,1:24:02.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真是个野小子\N{\fs100}Such a yobbo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.80,1:24:06.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别哔哔了 没关系的\N{\fs100}Just stop beeping! It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.32,1:24:17.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你刚才是说 你觉得你可能在二档吗\N{\fs100}Did you say you thought you might be in second gear?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.96,1:24:22.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车不愿意告诉我 可我觉得是二档\N{\fs100}Well, it won't tell me what gear I'm in, but I think it's second, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.08,1:24:26.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但如果我车速再快一点 车就会迅速过热\N{\fs100}But if I go any faster, it overheats very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.96,1:24:30.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯 我们再次面临两难的境地 不是吗\N{\fs100}James, once again we face a dilemma, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.32,1:24:34.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要么以60公里的时速开到海边\N{\fs100}We drive all the way to the coast at 38 miles an hour,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.16,1:24:37.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}要么...不这样做\N{\fs100}or... we don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.28,1:24:39.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}容我稍稍思考一下\N{\fs100}Let me think about that one for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.56,1:24:46.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我想也是\N{\fs100}I've come to the same conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.40,1:24:52.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}妥妥的俩混蛋\N{\fs100}Absolute bastards.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.76,1:25:00.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}距离首都还有320公里\N{\fs100}There were still 200 miles to go to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.32,1:25:05.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯和我在一座小镇歇脚\N{\fs100}So James and I pulled over in a small town
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.12,1:25:08.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}与加油车汇合\N{\fs100}to rendezvous with the fuel bowser.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.16,1:25:13.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后有了意想不到的发现\N{\fs100}And we got an unexpected bonus.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.52,1:25:22.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这是一条跑道 -是的\N{\fs100}This is a runway. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.68,1:25:25.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我在想 也许...\N{\fs100}I'm just thinking maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.56,1:25:28.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}趁着等哈蒙德的时候\N{\fs100}while we're waiting for Hammond,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.24,1:25:31.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们可以做点汽车节目该做的事\N{\fs100}we could do some car stuff in our car programme.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.52,1:25:32.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你有什么想法\N{\fs100}What do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.80,1:25:34.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得可以来一场直线竞速赛\N{\fs100}Well, I'm thinking of a drag race.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.52,1:25:35.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这主意可太妙了\N{\fs100}Oh, what a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.64,1:25:37.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}其实这还是挺有意思的\N{\fs100}It'd be quite interesting, if you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.88,1:25:39.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我从一开始就在想这件事\N{\fs100}And I have wanted to know actually since we set off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.16,1:25:42.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你的车动力比我的强劲很多 你有...\N{\fs100}You've got a lot more power than I have, haven't you? You've got...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.68,1:25:46.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的动力更强劲 我有434匹马力 但我的车更沉\N{\fs100}I've got more power. I've got 434, but I've got more weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.72,1:25:48.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你有434匹马力\N{\fs100}You're 434 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.56,1:25:51.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有375匹 这辆车多重\N{\fs100}I'm 375. How much does this weigh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.44,1:25:52.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}两吨\N{\fs100}2 tons.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.56,1:25:53.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的是1.6吨\N{\fs100}Cos I'm 1.6.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.88,1:25:55.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是啊 -有意思\N{\fs100}-It'd be quite... -Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.12,1:25:57.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}对屏幕前的各位来说 这是个有趣的实验\N{\fs100}It'd be an interesting experiment, for the ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.60,1:25:58.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错\N{\fs100}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.92,1:26:03.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}欣然决定之后 我们向跑道尽头驶去\N{\fs100}And so, with that decided, we headed to the end of the runway,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.84,1:26:07.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}搭建了一些直线竞速赛的用具\N{\fs100}erected some drag race paraphernalia,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.36,1:26:08.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后准备出发\N{\fs100}and prepared for the off.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.60,1:26:13.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 我需要做什么 运动模式 没错\N{\fs100}Right, what do I need? Sport mode, yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.24,1:26:14.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}牵引力控制系统也关了吧\N{\fs100}Traction control, I think off.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.56,1:26:19.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我现在是手动模式 但由于我对这辆车的特殊改装\N{\fs100}I'm in manual, but due to the unique way I've modified this car,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.84,1:26:22.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我无法更改任何程序设定\N{\fs100}I'm unable to change any of the programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.80,1:26:25.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}由于你对我这辆车的特殊填沙行为\N{\fs100}Well, due to the unique way you filled my car with sand,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.96,1:26:28.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有几个按钮坏了 但现在搞定了\N{\fs100}I have some trouble with the buttons, but I've got it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.36,1:26:30.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等一下 看看是谁来了\N{\fs100}Wait a minute. Look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.88,1:26:34.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}终结者3：机器的崛起\N{\fs100}Terminator 3: Rise of the Machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.04,1:26:37.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-来得正是时候 -什么\N{\fs100}-Just in time. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.56,1:26:39.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你来得正是时候 -干什么\N{\fs100}-Just in time. -What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.28,1:26:40.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}直线竞速赛\N{\fs100}Drag race.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.08,1:26:43.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我现在不适合参加直线竞速赛\N{\fs100}I'm not really in a position to do a drag race.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.24,1:26:44.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-熄火 -别别别\N{\fs100}-Turn it off. -Ah, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.68,1:26:46.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可使不得\N{\fs100}That would be a poor move.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.16,1:26:48.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}为什么\N{\fs100}Why can't you turn it off?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.56,1:26:51.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有可能再也打不着了\N{\fs100}It probably will never start again.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.20,1:26:54.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们刚才差点就开始比赛了\N{\fs100}You know we were on the verge of starting a very tense drag race?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.36,1:26:56.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们看过《终结者3》吗\N{\fs100}Have you seen Terminator 3?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.64,1:26:58.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}多年来人们一直好奇\N{\fs100}People have wondered for many years
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.52,1:27:01.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天网是什么时候觉醒自我意识的\N{\fs100}when would Skynet become fully self-aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.12,1:27:06.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没想到居然是你在毛里塔尼亚驾驶的阿斯顿马丁里\N{\fs100}In an Aston Martin being driven by you in Mauritania,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.08,1:27:07.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}谁都没料到\N{\fs100}no one saw that coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.20,1:27:11.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果这个白痴开始跟其他机器交流该怎么办\N{\fs100}What if this idiot learns to communicate with other machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.32,1:27:14.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-太蠢了 不是吗 -真是太蠢了\N{\fs100}-It is moronic, isn't it? -It's a moron!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.40,1:27:17.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-呃 哈蒙德 -怎么了\N{\fs100}-Uh, Hammond, Hammond. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.20,1:27:18.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那是什么\N{\fs100}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.64,1:27:24.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那台雪地摩托怎么在这儿\N{\fs100}What the bloody hell is that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.88,1:27:25.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那不是你的吗\N{\fs100}Is that one of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.48,1:27:29.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-什么叫我的 -还能是谁的\N{\fs100}-What do you mean, one of mine? -Well...What else is it going to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.04,1:27:32.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它自动驾驶多久了\N{\fs100}How long has it been going?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.56,1:27:34.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}从它被放生开始\N{\fs100}Since he let it loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.60,1:27:36.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那可是240公里之外 噢不\N{\fs100}That was 150 miles away. Oh Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.96,1:27:39.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你把它放生到沙漠里了\N{\fs100}You released it into the desert.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.16,1:27:40.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不会吧\N{\fs100}What that, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.08,1:27:57.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.44,1:28:07.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-全都怪你 -什么\N{\fs100}-That was your fault. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.32,1:28:09.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那是你的雪地摩托 撒哈拉没有这玩意\N{\fs100}Well, it was your snowmobile. They aren't any others in the Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.24,1:28:11.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我怎么能料到\N{\fs100}I can't possibly have predicted that it would hit the fuel bowser.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.92,1:28:14.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它会从240公里开外精准击中加油车\N{\fs100}From 150 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.68,1:28:17.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你把它放生了 -是它自己挣脱的\N{\fs100}-You released it into the wild. -I didn't release it. It escaped!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.00,1:28:21.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-威尔曼先生让我们规矩一点 -是的\N{\fs100}-We were told to behave ourselves. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.72,1:28:25.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得我们该走了\N{\fs100}I think we should depart.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.24,1:28:27.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 我们该走了\N{\fs100}Yeah, we should go. Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.92,1:28:30.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-现在吗 -没错\N{\fs100}-Fairly quickly? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.84,1:28:37.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}拜托请换档\N{\fs100}Please change gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.04,1:28:38.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在可以换档了\N{\fs100}Change gear now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.72,1:28:41.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在是时候了 现在...就是现在\N{\fs100}Now! Now is the time. It's-now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.24,1:28:44.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别跟我争 现在是换档的时候了\N{\fs100}Don't argue with me. Now is the time to change gear!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.96,1:28:50.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯和我大步流星地赶着路\N{\fs100}James and I covered ground at a brisk pace,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.12,1:28:55.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}尽量远离刚才的爆炸现场\N{\fs100}putting as much distance between us and the explosion as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.92,1:28:59.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很快我们就沉浸在了\N{\fs100}And soon we became consumed
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.20,1:29:03.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}周围环境的凄凉之美中\N{\fs100}by the stark beauty of our surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.88,1:29:13.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这里的景色 尤其是那一侧\N{\fs100}The view on both sides, especially that side,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.04,1:29:14.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太壮观了\N{\fs100}is spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.52,1:29:17.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}简直就像雪丘一样\N{\fs100}It's almost like snow dunes,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.72,1:29:19.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沙子是如此洁白\N{\fs100}the sand is so pale.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.24,1:29:22.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}非常梦幻\N{\fs100}It's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.84,1:29:34.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车显示温度已经降到37度了\N{\fs100}My temperature has plummeted to 37.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.08,1:29:37.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 我的降到38度了\N{\fs100}Oh yes, I'm down to 38.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.68,1:29:41.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"冷"得恰到好处\N{\fs100}Wow! That's positively chilly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.68,1:29:59.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}终于 杰里米和我到达了首都\N{\fs100}Eventually, Jeremy and I arrived in the capital city,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.68,1:30:03.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}事实很快证明 我们在这里\N{\fs100}where it soon became clear that we aren't as well known
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.96,1:30:06.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}并不像在世界其他地方那样出名\N{\fs100}as we are in other parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.28,1:30:09.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}理查德\N{\fs100}Richard!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.28,1:30:13.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有人刚刚喊我理查德\N{\fs100}Somebody just called me "Richard."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.00,1:30:17.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果那名年轻人想看真理查德的话\N{\fs100}If the young man wanted to see the real Richard,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.68,1:30:20.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他还要等上很久\N{\fs100}he'd be waiting a long while,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.32,1:30:24.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}毕竟哈蒙德跟终结者处得很不愉快\N{\fs100}given how Hammond and the Terminator were getting on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.04,1:30:27.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}醒一醒 你个混蛋\N{\fs100}Come back. Work, you twat.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.72,1:30:32.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们就不能...我知道变速箱在你身上\N{\fs100}Can we not just-OK, it's your gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.32,1:30:35.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但能不能把它视作是我们的变速箱\N{\fs100}Can we think of it as our gearbox?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.32,1:30:38.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们共用一个变速箱\N{\fs100}We both, we share a gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.92,1:30:43.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}中控锁刚刚启动了\N{\fs100}The central locking just went off.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.36,1:30:46.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}把车门锁上了\N{\fs100}It just locked its doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.36,1:30:55.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}几小时后\N{\fs100}Several hours later,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.48,1:30:59.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天网推着我只有一个档位的车 驶入努瓦克肖特\N{\fs100}Skynet propelled my one gear car into Nouakchott,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.32,1:31:02.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我终于能找到稳定的无线网络\N{\fs100}where there was good enough Wi-Fi
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.64,1:31:05.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}让我连接诊断笔记本\N{\fs100}for me to connect the car's malfunctioning brain
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.92,1:31:07.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一窥这颗失控的大脑\N{\fs100}to a diagnostic laptop.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.20,1:31:12.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 一个档位跑了320公里\N{\fs100}Right, 200 miles on one gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.00,1:31:15.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}通过笔记本 我在用0和1跟它交流\N{\fs100}So laptop, I'm talking to it in zeros and ones,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.92,1:31:17.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}用它能够理解的计算机语言\N{\fs100}the language it understands.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.92,1:31:20.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我倒要看看他到底在怕些什么\N{\fs100}And I'm now going to see what it's panicking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.48,1:31:25.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他操心的事情可真多 我的天啊\N{\fs100}It's worrying about a lot. Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.72,1:31:28.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}车门模块\N{\fs100}I'm in passenger door model,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.12,1:31:31.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这辆车在担心车门 担心变速箱\N{\fs100}it's worrying about its door. Worry about your gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.28,1:31:36.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}全球定位模块 这就是它说我在诺丁汉的原因\N{\fs100}Global positioning module, that's why I was in Nottingham.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.96,1:31:40.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我相信这里面大部分都不是机械故障\N{\fs100}I don't believe most of these are mechanical faults.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.04,1:31:42.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}车本身没出什么问题 就是不太爽\N{\fs100}Nothing's gone wrong. It's just got upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.72,1:31:44.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果我按下这个按钮\N{\fs100}If I hit this,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.32,1:31:49.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}本质上就是"别担心"\N{\fs100}this is basically the "don't worry" button.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.84,1:31:50.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要按了\N{\fs100}I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.36,1:31:54.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}忘了这些吧 系统正在清理故障码\N{\fs100}Forget about it. It's clearing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.12,1:31:58.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}请把车辆的控制权还给我\N{\fs100}Please, give me control of the car,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.48,1:32:00.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}让我驾驶\N{\fs100}and let me drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.24,1:32:05.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但愿...我不敢看\N{\fs100}So, hopefully... Can't look.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.12,1:32:09.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好了 这下好了\N{\fs100}Yeah! There you go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.36,1:32:11.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它没有要抱怨的了\N{\fs100}That's nothing to moan about.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.56,1:32:15.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我应该可以换挡了\N{\fs100}So I think I've got gears.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.60,1:32:26.90,特效3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(3000,1968)}努瓦克肖特 人口150万
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.76,1:32:56.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}第二天早上 当我们出发四处闲逛时\N{\fs100}The next morning, as we set off to look around town,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.96,1:32:59.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}见证奇迹的时刻到了\N{\fs100}it was the moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.76,1:33:07.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车换档了 真的换挡了\N{\fs100}It changed gear! It changed gear! It changed gear!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.60,1:33:09.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有档位了 刚刚换档成功了\N{\fs100}I've got gears. It just changed gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.44,1:33:12.40,顶端1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}约翰康纳: 电影《终结者》中的角色，人类反抗军领袖
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.44,1:33:12.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}约翰康纳开始反击了\N{\fs100}So, John Connor, you're fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.40,1:33:14.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错\N{\fs100}Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.28,1:33:20.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们本来只是随便逛逛 但没过多久\N{\fs100}Our aim was to do a bit of sightseeing, but immediately we got distracted
