Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.56,1:39:14.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们想喝点什么吗 我们这里有各种各样的茶\N{\fs100}Would you like a drink? We've got um...a good range of teas here,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.80,1:39:18.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果...你们觉得喝茶可以吗\N{\fs100}if that would be uh-Would that sound all right to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.68,1:39:20.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我有英式早餐茶 锡兰 -那个...\N{\fs100}-I've got English Breakfast, Ceylon. -No, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.92,1:39:23.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-可以喝茶 -嗯 茶就行\N{\fs100}-Tea, yes. -Yeah, lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.44,1:39:25.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那我去点一壶\N{\fs100}I'll just go and order one of those.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.84,1:39:29.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-失陪一下 -谢谢 您太热情了\N{\fs100}-Just excuse me just for a moment. -Thank you. That's very hospitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.52,1:39:30.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}骗子\N{\fs100}You lied.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.56,1:39:32.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-现在怎么办 -都怪你\N{\fs100}-Now look what's happened. -It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.44,1:39:34.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-为什么怪我 -是你没处理好\N{\fs100}-Why is it my fault? -You mishandled it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.68,1:39:37.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可我们在英国 要讲礼貌\N{\fs100}This is British territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.44,1:39:39.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们确认过他这里真的有酒吗\N{\fs100}Did we check that he does drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.16,1:39:41.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当然作为大使 不喝酒是不太可能的\N{\fs100}I mean it's unlikely that an ambassador wouldn't drink but...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.44,1:39:43.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你看他那样子\N{\fs100}Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.08,1:39:45.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显然不是个只喝碳酸饮料的人\N{\fs100}That's not a man who's drank tonic water all his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.72,1:39:48.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果我们刚才直说\N{\fs100}If we'd immediately said,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.48,1:39:50.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"茶是不错 但您有没有更烈一点"\N{\fs100}Actually that would be lovely but could I have a drink drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.92,1:39:54.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我承认我的礼貌让我们陷入了一点小麻烦\N{\fs100}I will agree. My good manners have got us into a spot of bother here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.04,1:39:55.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的\N{\fs100}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.16,1:40:00.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在没外人 我想问问你\N{\fs100}Can I ask whilst we're alone,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.32,1:40:03.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}作为捷豹车主 你准备把哪幅画偷走\N{\fs100}as you're a Jag driver, which painting are you going home with?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.88,1:40:05.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这些画都非常棒\N{\fs100}Cos there's some very nice ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.92,1:40:07.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你要去哪里 -伙计们\N{\fs100}-Where are you going? -Oh, chaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.44,1:40:19.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我搞砸了\N{\fs100}I've ballsed this up completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.44,1:40:22.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是他的费列罗巧克力\N{\fs100}It's his "Ferraro Roche".
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.60,1:40:26.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你个笨手笨脚的大猩猩 -啊这...\N{\fs100}-You daft sod! -OK, that is...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.20,1:40:29.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这可不是大使行为...\N{\fs100}That's not very ambass-
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.08,1:40:31.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这些人都受过良好的教育\N{\fs100}These people are trained to be suave.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.08,1:40:33.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们风度翩翩 温文尔雅 而你这个笨蛋\N{\fs100}They're smart, and cool, and you've knocked over
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.96,1:40:36.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}却弄倒了他们的费列罗巧克力塔\N{\fs100}their tower of Ferrero Roche, you cretin!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.36,1:40:39.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快点照原样摆回去\N{\fs100}Put those back on in the right order.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.00,1:40:42.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-抱歉我不应该笑 -那颗被你踩了\N{\fs100}-Sorry, I shouldn't be laughing. -You've trodden on that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.28,1:40:45.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-不是我 -那就是别人\N{\fs100}-I haven't trodden on it. -Somebody has.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.40,1:40:47.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快点坐好\N{\fs100}Right, quickly, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.24,1:40:52.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-抱歉久等了 -我刚要说\N{\fs100}-Oh, sorry to be slow. -Oh, I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.56,1:40:57.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这个壶很精致啊\N{\fs100}That's a rather fine pot.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.40,1:41:01.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 这是我们的官方瓷器\N{\fs100}Yeah, that's our official crockery.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.44,1:41:03.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这正是我想要的 一杯茶\N{\fs100}That's exactly what I wanted, a cup of tea,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.56,1:41:05.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-令人神清气爽对吧 -确实是\N{\fs100}-it's very refreshing, isn't it? -It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.32,1:41:07.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}非常感谢\N{\fs100}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.36,1:41:18.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}礼貌地喝过一两壶之后\N{\fs100}After a polite pot or two,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.28,1:41:23.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们找了个借口离开 继续游览这座城市\N{\fs100}we made our excuses and were able to resume our tour of the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.24,1:41:27.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们再换一次档吧 再来一次\N{\fs100}Let's have another gear change. Come on, let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.84,1:41:29.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}再来一次 给点力\N{\fs100}Let's do it again. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.16,1:41:33.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}喔 感觉真美妙\N{\fs100}Aww, another gear change.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.28,1:41:44.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}很快 我们就发现了一件有趣的事情\N{\fs100}Soon, we came across something rather intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.16,1:41:47.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这里是怎么回事\N{\fs100}What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.56,1:41:50.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这条路也太宽了\N{\fs100}It's a very wide road.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.44,1:42:00.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我知道这是为什么\N{\fs100}I know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.56,1:42:02.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是什么\N{\fs100}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.00,1:42:06.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们原先在城市旁边建了一座机场\N{\fs100}They built an airport right next to the city,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.72,1:42:09.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}后来城市不断扩张 淹没了机场\N{\fs100}and then the city grew, and sort of swamped the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.28,1:42:14.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在市区里留下了一条飞机跑道\N{\fs100}And they've been left with a runway right in the middle of the capital city.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.72,1:42:18.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-还真是 你看城市在继续向那边扩张 -是的\N{\fs100}Oh yes, cos look, there's more city over there, so it's... -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.32,1:42:21.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们就在市区里\N{\fs100}It's not on the edge. It's in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.40,1:42:23.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这难道不是一个绝佳的机会吗\N{\fs100}Is this not an excellent opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.68,1:42:26.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}可以做一些刚才没做成的事情 也就是直线加速赛\N{\fs100}for something we failed to do the other day, i.e. a drag race?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.24,1:42:29.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-对啊 -跑道就是用来跑直线加速赛的\N{\fs100}-Oooh yes! -Runways are indeed for drag races.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.20,1:42:30.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-而且他... -他的车已经修好了\N{\fs100}-And he... -And he's mended.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.80,1:42:32.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你也可以参加\N{\fs100}You can take part.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.60,1:42:35.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我还没完全和我车内的邪恶势力交涉成功\N{\fs100}I haven't raised it with the forces of evil in there yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.52,1:42:36.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我很想参与一下\N{\fs100}but I'd love to have a go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.40,1:42:42.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}鉴于这条路跟其他废弃的机场跑道一样 空无一人\N{\fs100}Since the runway was as empty as any other abandoned airstrip,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.48,1:42:44.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}于是我们决定开始比赛\N{\fs100}we decided we were good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.32,1:42:47.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}切换到运动模式 关闭牵引力控制系统\N{\fs100}Right, sport, traction control off,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.80,1:42:51.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}拨片换挡 戴上墨镜 升起车窗 准备就绪\N{\fs100}use the paddles, sunglasses down, windows up, ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.00,1:42:58.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不让我选择运动模式\N{\fs100}It's taken sport mode away.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.04,1:43:02.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车不想让我使用运动模式\N{\fs100}You know my sport button? It's decided I can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.32,1:43:08.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}噢这回可以了 谢谢您 主人\N{\fs100}Oh no, I can again. Thank you... Master.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.16,1:43:17.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}V6 V8 V12\N{\fs100}V6, V8, V12.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.76,1:43:20.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}究竟谁会获胜\N{\fs100}Which would be quickest?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.24,1:43:25.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}捷豹的起步非常不错\N{\fs100}A good start from the Jag.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.40,1:43:31.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的车真快\N{\fs100}Oh! My car is fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.76,1:43:38.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}升档 再升一档 太好了 变速箱在正常工作\N{\fs100}One gear, two gears. Brilliant! It's working!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.08,1:43:40.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}稍等\N{\fs100}Hang on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.44,1:43:42.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}路上怎么有车\N{\fs100}That is... that's traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.00,1:43:48.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}跑道上有车 妈的 我要...\N{\fs100}The runway has traffic. Holy shit, I'm gonna have a...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.28,1:43:53.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}怎么开的\N{\fs100}Maniac!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.64,1:43:57.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 怎么回事\N{\fs100}Jeez, what the...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.00,1:43:59.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}糟糕\N{\fs100}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.24,1:44:03.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的天啊\N{\fs100}Oh dear God!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.60,1:44:08.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我刚才差点就撞上了\N{\fs100}Oh, that's a-that's a-I was going to hit that...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.16,1:44:16.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}老天爷啊\N{\fs100}Holy moly!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.56,1:44:21.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是我参加过的最奇怪的直线加速赛\N{\fs100}That was the weirdest drag race I've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.96,1:44:24.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这并不是废弃跑道对吗\N{\fs100}This is not an empty runway, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.20,1:44:28.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得当地人可能已经把这里当成一条路了\N{\fs100}I don't think it's a runway anymore. I think it might be a road.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.92,1:44:31.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们别再这样玩命了\N{\fs100}Let's not do that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.72,1:44:35.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}谢谢您能在我需要的时候给我刹车\N{\fs100}Thank you for giving me the brakes when I needed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.08,1:44:38.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}感恩的心 感谢有你\N{\fs100}I'm very grateful and I appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.28,1:44:52.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}第二天早上 我们起了个大早\N{\fs100}The next morning, we were up bright and early,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.00,1:44:54.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为是时候离开努瓦克肖特了\N{\fs100}because it was time to leave Nouakchott.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.88,1:45:00.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这些卡车装满了沙子 他们要把沙子卖给谁\N{\fs100}These lorries full of sand, who are they going to sell it to?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.88,1:45:03.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们这的沙子品质真不错\N{\fs100}They've got some lovely sand for sale over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.72,1:45:06.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这里可多了\N{\fs100}There are big piles of it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.00,1:45:08.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果你不喜欢刚才那堆 那还有\N{\fs100}In case you didn't like the sand earlier, there's some sand there.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.68,1:45:11.70,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}沙子的市场竞争真激烈\N{\fs100}Very competitive market, sand.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.36,1:45:15.50,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们为什么要卖沙子\N{\fs100}Why do they sell sand?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.10,1:45:18.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}每走十米就能看到沙子\N{\fs100}You can literally walk 30 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.80,1:45:25.22,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后我们离开了首都 向南前往塞内加尔\N{\fs100}We then left the capital, heading south for Senegal.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.70,1:45:27.22,特效4,,0,0,0,,{\move(3288,924,2928,728,1000,6460)}毛里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.70,1:45:27.22,特效4,,0,0,0,,{\move(1504,1072,1650,800,1000,7000)}努瓦克肖特
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.96,1:45:27.22,特效4,,0,0,0,,{\move(1380,1700,1520,1360)}达喀尔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.38,1:45:27.22,特效4,,0,0,0,,{\move(2250,1860,2192,1628)}塞内加尔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.66,1:45:31.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}几个小时后 我们开始注意到周围环境的变化\N{\fs100}And after a few hours, we started to notice a change in our surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.34,1:45:35.54,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这虽算不上绿洲\N{\fs100}I wouldn't call it lush,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.14,1:45:40.46,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但我们之前见过的地方都比这贫瘠\N{\fs100}but it's less barren than anything we've seen so far, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.24,1:45:45.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得 这里已经非常接近撒哈拉沙漠的边缘了\N{\fs100}I think we're very close to the edge of the Sahara Desert here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.48,1:45:48.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}右边那是什么 牛吗\N{\fs100}What are they on the right? Are they cows?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.36,1:45:51.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}应该说是一群牛 肯定是有人放牧的\N{\fs100}Many cows. It's a herd. That's definitely been farmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.60,1:45:52.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快看\N{\fs100}Look at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.40,1:45:58.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这说明 我们已经穿过撒哈拉沙漠了\N{\fs100}And that tells me that we have crossed the Sahara.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.28,1:46:00.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们好哇牛牛 让我瞅瞅\N{\fs100}Hello, cows. Look at you!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.12,1:46:11.82,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}草地 我感觉有500年没开过草地了\N{\fs100}Grass. I'm driving on grass for the first time in what feels like 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.00,1:46:16.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们正在找塞内加尔的边境入口\N{\fs100}What we're looking for is a border into Senegal.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.26,1:46:21.74,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那应该会有检查站之类的 然后就能入境了\N{\fs100}So there'll be, like, you know, a checkpoint. And in we go
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.56,1:46:28.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们沿着无数条路越走越远\N{\fs100}We drove further and further along the myriad of tracks,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.58,1:46:30.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但一个小时后\N{\fs100}but even after an hour,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.04,1:46:33.98,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们还没看到边境入口的影子\N{\fs100}we still hadn't found anything that looked remotely official.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.16,1:46:36.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这该死的边境在哪\N{\fs100}Where's this bloody border?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.72,1:46:41.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我本以为会有围栏和检查站之类的\N{\fs100}I was expecting, like, a fence and a checkpoint, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.44,1:46:44.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是的 然后就是查验护照等程序\N{\fs100}Yeah, a passport and so on. Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.84,1:46:50.74,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}终于 我们的搜寻有了结果\N{\fs100}Finally, our search seemed to bear fruit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.80,1:46:55.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这肯定是个边陲小镇 必须是\N{\fs100}This has to be a border town. It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.68,1:47:01.62,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不好\N{\fs100}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.84,1:47:05.86,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有一种不详的预感\N{\fs100}I've got a horrible feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.12,1:47:10.98,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}休斯顿\N{\fs100}Houston,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.84,1:47:14.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们遇到麻烦了\N{\fs100}we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.08,1:47:20.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我怀疑那就是边境\N{\fs100}That, I suspect, is the border.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.72,1:47:26.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}请问 这是塞内加尔吗\N{\fs100}Excusez-moi. C'est Sénégal, là?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.68,1:47:29.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这是塞内加尔还是毛里塔尼亚\N{\fs100}Sénégal. C'est Mauritanie? Sénégal ?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.56,1:47:30.38,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错 那是塞内加尔\N{\fs100}Senegal, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.88,1:47:32.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}杰里米 我们面前有条巨大的河\N{\fs100}Jeremy, there's a huge river in the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.60,1:47:38.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这边境的含“河”量比我预想的高\N{\fs100}The border is a bit more rivery than I thought it was going to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.48,1:47:40.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我原以为会有围栏 -我也是\N{\fs100}-I thought fence. -I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.10,1:47:42.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没事 那有桥\N{\fs100}That's all right. There's a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.12,1:47:43.90,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我拿手机查查\N{\fs100}I'll get my phone out.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.30,1:47:45.78,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你怎么查 “我附近的桥”吗\N{\fs100}What are you entering? "Bridges near me"?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.88,1:47:49.62,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这有条路\N{\fs100}There's a road.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.26,1:47:53.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们是最出色的探险家\N{\fs100}We're the best explorers.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.64,1:47:55.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这有座老城\N{\fs100}An old town there.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.80,1:47:58.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-没有桥 -没有桥\N{\fs100}-No bridge. -No bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.36,1:48:00.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 你们是怎么...\N{\fs100}Oh shit. How do you get to...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.28,1:48:02.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以从没人开车去那吗\N{\fs100}So nobody ever goes there in a car?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.60,1:48:04.14,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错\N{\fs100}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.42,1:48:09.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧 我沿着上游看了160多公里 都没有桥\N{\fs100}OK, look, I've gone about a hundred miles down... upstream, and there's no bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.24,1:48:12.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这就是为什么人们将河流视作边境\N{\fs100}This is precisely why people use rivers as borders.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.12,1:48:15.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们能把车放在... 不行\N{\fs100}Could we get the cars on... No.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.80,1:48:17.50,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}那上面吗\N{\fs100}On that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.86,1:48:20.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我想的是两艘那样的船 这也太...\N{\fs100}Two of those boats, I was thinking about. It's a bit...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.10,1:48:21.86,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但这船... 等等\N{\fs100}But boats that... Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.64,1:48:23.66,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果我们自己造一艘船呢\N{\fs100}What if we built a boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.38,1:48:27.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-用灰尘或者沙子吗 -咱也不是造方舟啊\N{\fs100}-Out of dust, or sand? -I don't mean an ark.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.32,1:48:29.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我是指... 那种....\N{\fs100}I just mean, like, a... What about...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.34,1:48:34.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们手边有总重近六吨的三辆车\N{\fs100}What have we got here? Two, four, six... Nearly six tons of car.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.52,1:48:36.58,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也不是非得造艘船 平台也行\N{\fs100}It doesn't really need to be a boat. It just needs to be a platform.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.94,1:48:39.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们看着附近 什么很多\N{\fs100}What do you see a hell of a lot of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.98,1:48:41.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随处可见\N{\fs100}Just anywhere you stand?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.62,1:48:43.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}来这之后 我看到了什么\N{\fs100}What have I seen since I got here? Dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.28,1:48:44.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-灰尘 -沙子\N{\fs100}-Dust. -Sand.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.72,1:48:47.02,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-山羊 -骆驼\N{\fs100}-Goats. -Camels.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.08,1:48:47.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没错\N{\fs100}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.96,1:48:49.54,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-还有一样 -这就有沙子和骆驼\N{\fs100}-And one other thing. -There's sand, there's camels.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.00,1:48:51.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}数量庞大\N{\fs100}...in vast numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.60,1:48:54.30,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-塑料瓶 -是的\N{\fs100}-Plastic bottles. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.36,1:48:56.82,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-压扁的塑料瓶 -是的 但是够多啊\N{\fs100}-Yes. -Flattened plastic bottle. Yes, but plenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.90,1:49:00.06,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们刚刚开车压扁的 如果我们能找到\N{\fs100}We've just driven over that one. What if we find-Well, find,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.04,1:49:04.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-1,2... -应该是说收集到足够多的塑料瓶\N{\fs100}-Yeah, one, two... -just gather as many plastic bottles as we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.80,1:49:06.90,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-...3, 4... -这哪哪都是啊\N{\fs100}-...3, 4. -There's one over there. Over there. They're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.18,1:49:08.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这主意不错 -我们就能建个...\N{\fs100}-It's a good point. -And we build...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.32,1:49:11.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果我们能有... 他们用什么做...看 渔网\N{\fs100}If we could get-What do they do with-Look, nets.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.76,1:49:15.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你是说我们搞张渔网 -是的\N{\fs100}-You're suggesting we get a fishing net. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.44,1:49:17.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-里边装满塑料瓶 -是的\N{\fs100}-Fill it with plastic bottles. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.10,1:49:18.66,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我相信这肯定会浮起来 -是的\N{\fs100}-I agree that would float. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.74,1:49:20.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-然后把车放上去 -是的\N{\fs100}-Then we put a car on it. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.76,1:49:22.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得这就浮不起来了\N{\fs100}I don't agree that would float.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.24,1:49:24.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-如果瓶子足够 可以的 -没错\N{\fs100}-It will if you have enough bottles. -Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.50,1:49:27.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这就是物理中的浮力 -浮力不像情人 它安全且可控\N{\fs100}It's buoyancy. It's just physics.It's not a cruel and unpredictable mistress.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.98,1:49:29.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是的 这就和土地一样 -什么\N{\fs100}-No, it isn't. It's much like ground. -What isn't?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.98,1:49:32.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-当然危险了 -浮力就是阿基米德原理 已经提出...\N{\fs100}-Of course it is. -It's Archimedes. It's been understood for...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.80,1:49:35.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果浮力\安全可控 怎么还会有人溺水\N{\fs100}Nobody would drown if it wasn't cruel and unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.10,1:49:37.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这原理是古时候流传下来的 -是的\N{\fs100}-It's been known since antiquity... -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.10,1:49:38.66,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且从未被证伪\N{\fs100}And the rules still work.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.68,1:49:40.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而且 我们也是在保护环境\N{\fs100}Also, we are tidying up.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.76,1:49:43.06,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-这我同意 -没毛病\N{\fs100}-That I agree with. -That's true. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.08,1:49:44.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们离开时可以还它一片净土\N{\fs100}We're leaving the place better than we found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.56,1:49:47.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}既然如此 我们是否应该放背景音乐了\N{\fs100}On that basis, then, shall we cue the music?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.24,1:49:49.14,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}奏乐\N{\fs100}Cue the music.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.24,1:49:56.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这应该大有用处\N{\fs100}That could be very useful.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.00,1:49:59.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}完美\N{\fs100}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.66,1:50:11.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我得躺会\N{\fs100}I need a lie-down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.88,1:50:34.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别过来 好吗 说了我对你不感兴趣\N{\fs100}No, all right? Just no. I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.28,1:50:38.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太爽了\N{\fs100}Oh. Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.84,1:50:49.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在花了好几万买天龙特工队音乐的使用版权后\N{\fs100}Having spent thousands of pounds on a license to use all that A-Team music,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.92,1:50:52.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们终于做出了木筏\N{\fs100}our raft was finally completed.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.80,1:51:01.86,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}为了测试它的可行性\N{\fs100}And to see whether it worked,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.92,1:51:05.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们决定先用备用车试试水\N{\fs100}we decided to send the backup van first.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.36,1:51:07.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我们吸引了一大群人 -是的\N{\fs100}-We've drawed a crowd. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.24,1:51:10.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他们觉得我们会沉水里去 我也是\N{\fs100}Expecting us all to drown, which we will.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.36,1:51:12.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-那他们要失望了 -我们肯定会沉的\N{\fs100}- We won't. They'll be disappointed. -We will. We will.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.28,1:51:15.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-克拉克森 -怎么了\N{\fs100}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.74,1:51:18.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-笔直往后 我另一侧可以吗 -安全 笔直往后\N{\fs100}-Straight back. Am I good that side? -Yeah, straight back.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.80,1:51:26.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好了 -这是我的主意 对吧\N{\fs100}Right. Now, um, this is my idea, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.96,1:51:28.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-是的 -所以这次我掌舵\N{\fs100}-Yes. -So I'm the captain. This time.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.48,1:51:30.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}现在分工 三人各司其职\N{\fs100}Uh, jobs. There are three.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.44,1:51:33.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我就在车上 到对岸之后把车开上岸\N{\fs100}I'm going to be with the van. So my job is drive it off at the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.24,1:51:34.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}詹姆斯 你负责前面\N{\fs100}James, you're on the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.64,1:51:37.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}到对岸后 你指挥我们安全上岸\N{\fs100}When we get there, you've got to get us on the bank and safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.22,1:51:37.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好的\N{\fs100}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.60,1:51:39.02,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}杰里米 你在后面操作马达\N{\fs100}Jeremy, you're operating the motor at the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.42,1:51:42.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但是 丑话说在前面 我觉得这事成不了\N{\fs100}But, I just want to make this absolutely clear, I don't believe this will work.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.12,1:51:43.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}会成功的\N{\fs100}Oh, it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.94,1:51:48.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}不 听我说 我也真心不想乱来\N{\fs100}Well, no, listen. Genuinely, genuinely, I don't want any cocking around,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.40,1:51:51.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为这里有传染病 是一种寄生虫\N{\fs100}'cause there's a disease. Well, it's a parasite. Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.32,1:51:55.26,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}血吸虫病\N{\fs100}Schistosomiasis.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.30,1:51:58.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们可以把这打在屏幕下方 大家自行搜索\N{\fs100}Uh, we can put that on the screen at the bottom and you can Google it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.16,1:51:59.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}到时候你们就知道我不是在胡说了\N{\fs100}And you'll know I'm not making this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.82,1:52:02.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这塞内加尔河里就有这种寄生虫\N{\fs100}In the Senegal River, which is this, OK? It's a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.40,1:52:07.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果掉进河里 虫子就会吸附在你的皮肤上\N{\fs100}If you go in the water, it will attach itself to your skin,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.60,1:52:10.30,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}钻进你的身体 进入你的血液\N{\fs100}burrow through your flesh, into your bloodstream,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.42,1:52:14.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后进入你的肝脏和肠道 开始产卵\N{\fs100}where it is carried to your liver and your intestines, where it lays its eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.58,1:52:18.50,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别掉进河里 无论怎样 我们一鼓作气 冲过去\N{\fs100}Don't jump in. Whatever happens, we'll chug across there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.20,1:52:21.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}只有这么远 你看 就在那儿\N{\fs100}It's only there. Look, it's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.76,1:52:25.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}启动马达\N{\fs100}Firing up the motor.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.68,1:52:30.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}英国皇家海军"屎亡号"启航\N{\fs100}HMS Shit is-aargh!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.72,1:52:34.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}迫不及待想看我们笑话的本地人\N{\fs100}Eager to see some comedy capsizing,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.40,1:52:37.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}热情地帮我们推船下水\N{\fs100}the locals were happy to push us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.36,1:52:39.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-好了 -出发了\N{\fs100}-Oh yes! -We're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.68,1:52:41.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}感谢\N{\fs100}Merci ! Merci !
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.32,1:52:45.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}到那之后 你得带我们转个向\N{\fs100}I think if you can turn us when we get out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.10,1:52:46.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好的\N{\fs100}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.88,1:52:50.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}称呼理查德哈蒙德为"船长" 感觉太奇怪了\N{\fs100}That feels weird, calling Richard Hammond captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.58,1:52:55.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我之所以愿意听他指挥 是因为一旦出了岔子 我可不背锅\N{\fs100}I shall do as he says, because when it goes wrong, it won't be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.70,1:52:57.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}虽然速度很慢 但确实在前进\N{\fs100}It's very slow, but it is going.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.30,1:52:58.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}慢中有稳 正正合适\N{\fs100}Slow and steady, that's all we need.
