Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.00,2:00:00.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}唯独到不了心心念的彼岸\N{\fs100}except the beach we were headed for.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.16,2:00:04.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我正在朝错误的方向横向漂移 就是这么个情况\N{\fs100}I'm drifting sideways in the wrong direction, is what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.32,2:00:08.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我做出了两次超大的U形掉头\N{\fs100}What I've done is two enormous U-turns.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.12,2:00:11.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当地人以为我们疯了\N{\fs100}The locals think we're deranged.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.44,2:00:17.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它把我又带回毛里塔尼亚了\N{\fs100}It's taking me back to Mauritania.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.96,2:00:19.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我不想回去\N{\fs100}I don't want to go back to Mauritania.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.04,2:00:23.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有人能告诉我那边有什么吗 我正往那去\N{\fs100}Can anybody tell me what's down here, because that's where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.00,2:00:24.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是大海\N{\fs100}The sea.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.48,2:00:29.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我完全卡在角落里了 两侧都是墙\N{\fs100}I'm completely stuck in a corner with walls on two sides of me.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.20,2:00:32.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}转啊 你个混蛋\N{\fs100}Turn, you bastard, turn.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.48,2:00:38.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我欣赏她淡定洗衣服的样子 好像这种喜剧每天都会发生\N{\fs100}I love the way she's just doing her washing, as though this happens every single day.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.80,2:00:42.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}该死 不好了\N{\fs100}Oh, bloody hell, no. Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.28,2:00:43.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我的天啊\N{\fs100}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:44.76,2:00:46.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}别再撞我了\N{\fs100}Stop crashing into me!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.44,2:00:48.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我又回到芦苇丛了\N{\fs100}I'm back in the reeds!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.72,2:00:52.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}刚才有人驶向过正确方向吗 哪怕只有一会\N{\fs100}Has anybody managed to go the right way at any point?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.12,2:00:53.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}没有\N{\fs100}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.08,2:00:58.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}再次挣脱芦苇之后\N{\fs100}Having freed myself from the reeds again,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.20,2:01:01.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我有一项关于舵的重大发现\N{\fs100}I made an important steering-related discovery.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.44,2:01:06.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果龟速前进 我是说 空档蠕动\N{\fs100}If you go incredibly slowly, I mean, tick over, OK,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.40,2:01:10.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就可以向右了 一旦提速 就会变成向左转\N{\fs100}you can turn right. If you increase speed, you go left.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.72,2:01:22.40,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}随着所有人应用了我的新发现\N{\fs100}With all of us deploying my new discovery,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.40,2:01:25.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们很快就朝着正确的方向前进\N{\fs100}we were soon heading in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.56,2:01:29.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}太棒了\N{\fs100}Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:30.36,2:01:34.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要成功了 正在驶向对岸\N{\fs100}I am going to do it. I am heading for the shore.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.92,2:01:36.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}走起来\N{\fs100}Drive, drive!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.36,2:01:40.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我闻到啤酒味了\N{\fs100}I can smell beer!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.44,2:01:46.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}聪明如我 明白靠岸需要大量的动力\N{\fs100}Being intelligent, I knew I'd need a big burst of power to get ashore.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.80,2:01:51.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}于是 我升起车顶 保护脑子免受寄生虫的侵害\N{\fs100}So I raised my roof to protect my head from the parasites.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.60,2:01:59.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真不错啊\N{\fs100}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.84,2:02:09.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我快到了\N{\fs100}I'm so nearly there!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.64,2:02:12.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}求你了 就这一次 往左吧\N{\fs100}Please, just for once, go left.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.12,2:02:17.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我靠岸了\N{\fs100}Oh, I've hit the bank.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.56,2:02:21.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们的前轮进入了塞内加尔 这算吗\N{\fs100}Our front wheels are in Senegal, does that count?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.24,2:02:25.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我觉得肯定开到了塞内加尔 是的 我们到了\N{\fs100}Oh, I think we're definitely in Senegal, yeah, I think we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.72,2:02:33.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显然 将这三辆车改回去 我们还有工作要做\N{\fs100}Obviously, there is work to be done returning these to be normal land-based vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.16,2:02:36.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但有一些更重要的事 我们需要优先处理\N{\fs100}but there's something more important to attend to first.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.20,2:02:53.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}你们俩跟我不一样\N{\fs100}You two are different to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.72,2:02:56.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我看着这杯啤酒 会想\N{\fs100}I look at that and I just think,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.84,2:02:59.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"多么伟大的发明!"\N{\fs100}"Oh, what an invention!"
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.60,2:03:03.56,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看着它 品味它\N{\fs100}Now, looking at it, savouring it,
