Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.60,2:03:13.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看看杯子上凝结的水珠 看看翻腾的气泡\N{\fs100}Look at the condensation on the glass, look at the bubbles,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.68,2:03:16.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}看看...品味一下这种期待\N{\fs100}look at the... Savour the anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.92,2:03:20.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}因为在我看来 这也一样美\N{\fs100}Because in my mind, it's as good.
