Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.68,2:03:26.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-很烦吗 \N{\fs100}It's annoying?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.64,2:03:29.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我看到了尤物 听到了胡话\N{\fs100}I'm just seeing beauty, hearing bollocks.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.92,2:03:35.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显然 我们决定多喝几杯\N{\fs100}Obviously, we decided to have more than one.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.56,2:03:39.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}自然 随着哈蒙德开始喝上下一轮\N{\fs100}So, as Hammond was getting the next round in,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.28,2:03:45.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我溜到他的车上 搞了一点终结者风格的恶作剧\N{\fs100}I slipped out to his car for a bit of Terminator-based mischief.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.72,2:03:48.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}如果把我的手机 蓝牙连接到这台扬声器\N{\fs100}If I Bluetooth my phone to this speaker
