Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.00,2:03:53.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我就可以给他播放消息\N{\fs100}I can play messages to him
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.92,2:03:57.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}他会以为车在对话\N{\fs100}and he'll think his car is talking to him.
