Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.40,2:05:29.76,特效4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1392,1660)}达喀尔
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.44,2:05:34.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}在我们史诗般的旅程即将结束之际\N{\fs100}And with our epic trip this close to the end,
