Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.60,2:07:00.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们之前每次冒险时驾驶过的车辆 我都非常喜爱\N{\fs100}I've been fond of cars we've used on these adventures in the past,
