Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.48,2:07:37.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们正驶向达喀尔\N{\fs100}On the way to Dakar,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.80,2:07:42.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}也就是世界上 最激动人心 最艰难比赛的终点\N{\fs100}the finishing point for the most dramatic and gruelling race in the world.
