Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.96,2:08:30.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}它仍然会闪闪发亮 但会陷入宿命 \N{\fs100}It would have stayed shiny and nice, but it would have become what it is,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.76,2:08:33.94,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}一辆略显过时 缓缓凋零\N{\fs100}which is a slightly outdated, slowly fading example
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.94,2:08:36.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}曾经辉煌过的豪华跑车\N{\fs100}of a once-grand grand tourer.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.52,2:08:39.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}通过我的改装\N{\fs100}By doing what I've done to it,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.24,2:08:43.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我能够将它带到这里 做一些了不起的事情\N{\fs100}I've been able to bring it out here to do something incredible.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.96,2:08:46.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}而这些经历如今都镌刻在车身上\N{\fs100}And those experiences are now written across it
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.12,2:08:49.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}显示在划痕 擦痕 凹痕和裂缝之中\N{\fs100}in scuffs and scrapes and dents and cracks.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.00,2:08:54.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这些是它的命脉 是它脸上的笑纹\N{\fs100}They are its lifelines, its laughter-lines on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.20,2:08:56.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我很喜欢它\N{\fs100}And I love it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.24,2:09:00.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}之前它并不特别 但现在 足够特别了\N{\fs100}I made it special. It wasn't special. Now it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.84,2:09:24.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们开到了极其美丽的圣路易斯  这座小城的海岸线上\N{\fs100}We hit the coast in the surprisingly pretty town of St Louis
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.32,2:09:30.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}然后一路向南 与大西洋平行前进\N{\fs100}and turned south, running parallel with the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.84,2:09:34.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这给我了灵感\N{\fs100}Which gave me an idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.04,2:09:40.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我们为什么不像以前那样 从沙滩进入达喀尔\N{\fs100}Why don't we go into Dakar on the beach, like they used to?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.76,2:09:44.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}拉力赛的终点设置在沙滩上\N{\fs100}On the rally? It was finished on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.88,2:09:47.08,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}对啊\N{\fs100}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.92,2:09:52.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}当然 我的同事们没有任何异议\N{\fs100}Naturally, my colleagues had no objections whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.00,2:09:59.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}所以 我们转头驶入沙滩 完成最后的112公里\N{\fs100}So we turned onto the sand to complete the last 70 miles,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.72,2:10:02.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}就像过去的赛车手一样\N{\fs100}just as the races of the past had done.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:26.12,2:10:27.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}机械增压启动\N{\fs100}Supercharger engaged.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.68,2:10:38.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快看那边\N{\fs100}Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.44,2:10:43.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}巴黎达喀尔拉力赛 这就是终点\N{\fs100}Paris-Dakar! This is the finish!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.44,2:10:54.52,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}正是为了看到这特别的时刻\N{\fs100}It will be for these exact moments that people
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.52,2:10:59.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}人们才会忍受巴黎达喀尔拉力赛 一路走来的苦难和艰辛\N{\fs100}endured the suffering and hardship of doing the Paris-Dakar.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.00,2:11:00.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}参赛就是为了这一刻\N{\fs100}This is what they did it for. This!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.92,2:11:09.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我要和理查德"鼹鼠"哈蒙德 并肩前行\N{\fs100}I'm going to pull alongside Richard "The Hamster" Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:12.16,2:11:14.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}快看 我们开进海报了\N{\fs100}Look at this! We're in a poster!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.88,2:11:18.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}我谢谢您\N{\fs100}Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.36,2:11:32.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}从来没有玩得这么开心过\N{\fs100}Never had so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:37.16,2:11:40.24,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}今天太美好了\N{\fs100}What a wonderful, wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.56,2:11:43.64,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}有短信\N{\fs100}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.60,2:11:46.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}威尔曼先生发来的\N{\fs100}Text message from Mr Wilman.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.36,2:11:52.28,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}"进入达喀尔之前 你们可能想看一下新闻推送"\N{\fs100}"Before going into Dakar, you might want to check your news feeds."
Dialogue: 0,2:11:54.36,2:11:55.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}真的吗\N{\fs100}Really?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.68,2:11:59.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}英国广播公司新闻\N{\fs100}BBC News.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.12,2:12:06.97,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}气候变化 全是气候变化\N{\fs100}Climate change, climate change, climate change.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:07.60,2:12:09.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}洪水 气候变化\N{\fs100}Floods, climate change.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.04,2:12:11.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}试试推特\N{\fs100}Try Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.80,2:12:17.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊\N{\fs100}Oh, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.44,2:12:21.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等等 请回话 怎么停车了\N{\fs100}Hang on. Coming. Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.12,2:12:26.20,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}怎么停车了\N{\fs100}Why have you stopped?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:27.56,2:12:29.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}威尔曼刚刚让我们看新闻\N{\fs100}Wilman just said, "Check your news feeds."
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.20,2:12:34.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这发生在达喀尔\N{\fs100}That's Dakar.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.92,2:12:37.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}什么\N{\fs100}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.80,2:12:41.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}达喀尔 发生了重大骚乱\N{\fs100}Dakar. There's proper major riots.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:42.72,2:12:44.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}已经开始了\N{\fs100}It's kicked off.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.04,2:12:47.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}天啊 骚乱的原因是什么\N{\fs100}Oh, geez. What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.12,2:12:51.60,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}谁知道 就是一些政治...我不知道\N{\fs100}God knows. It's some political... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.60,2:12:54.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-有很多... -这是...我知道...\N{\fs100}-There's a lot of... -I know there's a lot, it's...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:54.72,2:12:57.72,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-有燃烧的公共汽车 应该... -天啊\N{\fs100}-And it's burning buses. -Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.24,2:12:59.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-你看这个了吗 -没有\N{\fs100}-Have you seen this? -No.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.36,2:13:01.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}达喀尔\N{\fs100}Dakar.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.24,2:13:06.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}骚乱已经开始了 还有枪战\N{\fs100}It's properly kicked off. There are gun battles.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.60,2:13:09.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-还有火 有烧着的公共汽车 -是的\N{\fs100}And there's fire. There's a bus on fire. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.08,2:13:13.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}好吧\N{\fs100}Um... right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.36,2:13:18.16,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这种情况不能带团队进去\N{\fs100}You can't take the crew down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.16,2:13:20.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30} 不能 谁都不应该... 我不想让任何人去\N{\fs100}No, I know. Nobody sh-I don't want anyone going down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.88,2:13:23.88,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我觉得不应该... -我之前知道有计划中的抗议行动\N{\fs100}I mean, I knew there were some protests planned,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:23.88,2:13:26.00,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}但应该是三四天之后\N{\fs100}but that's about three or four days.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.00,2:13:28.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}是为了抗议反对派 但显然提前开始了\N{\fs100}It's over that opposition, but it's obviously kicked off early.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.76,2:13:32.77,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-但这是眼下发生的事 -也可能是别的原因 已经开始了\N{\fs100}-That's now. -Or this is something else. Or it's getting ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.77,2:13:34.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这样的话情况会更恶劣\N{\fs100}which means it's going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.72,2:13:40.96,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}等一下 我们的返程航班从达喀尔起飞\N{\fs100}Wait a minute. Our flight home is from Dakar.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:40.96,2:13:42.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}确实\N{\fs100}It is.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.04,2:13:44.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-飞不成了 -不能飞了\N{\fs100}-Well, we can't do that. -It's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.08,2:13:47.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-圣路易斯机场关闭了 -什么\N{\fs100}-St Louis Airport's closed. -What?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:47.44,2:13:49.84,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-圣路易斯机场关闭了 -关闭了\N{\fs100}-St Louis Airport's closed. -It's closed?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.84,2:13:52.36,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}已关闭 正在整修 我刚查了\N{\fs100}Closed. Refurbishment. Checked it.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.88,2:14:00.04,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这意味着 我们必须开车返回努瓦克肖特\N{\fs100}That means we've got to drive back to Nouakchott.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:01.56,2:14:04.76,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-真的吗 这是唯一选择了? -反正我不去达喀尔\N{\fs100}Seriously? Is that the only option? Well, I'm not going to Dakar.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.92,2:14:08.32,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}来嘛 很有趣的\N{\fs100}Come on, it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.32,2:14:11.48,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这就是一场往返式拉力赛了 这么着吧\N{\fs100}It's a there and back rally. Right, then.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.72,2:14:21.12,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}这倒表示了一件事\N{\fs100}It does mean one thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.00,2:14:25.17,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}-我可以用传统结束语了 -没错\N{\fs100}-I can use the traditional ending. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.17,2:14:26.68,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}伴随着这糟糕的失望之情\N{\fs100}On that terrible disappointment,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.68,2:14:27.92,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}节目该结束了\N{\fs100} it's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.64,2:14:30.44,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}感谢大家的观看 下次再见\N{\fs100}See you next time. Thanks for watching.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.44,2:14:34.80,字幕1080,,0,0,0,,{\be30}糟透了\N{\fs100}F-ing hell.
